    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTdebrisCidaRequest": "Come to the backwoods stairs, I have a request for you. ~Anonymous",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTdebrisCidaAlmostDone": "Hey! Good news: The debris will be removed tomorrow! Come to the backwoods stairs again, we'll be waiting for you!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailBundle1Done": "^Good morning, Sweetpea!^Me and my dear husband were walking on the forest, until we saw you leaving that old house with a Bouquet Maker. You looked confused on how to use it, so let granny explain a few things...^To make it work, you'll need cloth and three beautiful flowers.^Then, put them on the machine and wait 10 minutes until it's done... Quick, isn't it?^After that, you can gift it to your loved one and watch their reaction! Eheheheh...^Also, my dear Raoni was able to find some extra cloth here and we decided to give it to you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailBundle1Done2": "A gift from Mayara and Raoni:",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailBundle2Done": "^Hello, dear!^I believe you've already found a Perfumaker, so let me teach you how to use it...^First, you will need Cereal Alcohol to make it work, it is the base of all perfumes... You can make more Cereal Alcohol by putting rice on the oil maker!^Second step, you can add any fruit or flower you like! Personally, I love plum perfume...^Then, you must be patient and wait for a few days until it's ready.^After that, you may, sell, use or even gift it to someone you like!^I had some Cereal Alcohol here and think you will make a good use of it!^Kisses from Serena!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailBundle2Done2": "A gift from Serena:",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailBundle3Done": "^Hey, it's Levi.^I saw you carrying a Chocolatier to your farm yesterday, let me explain to you how to use it.^You'll need choco powder to make it work. You're lucky I have some extra here.^To make more choco powder, you DO NOT place it on the mill, you must buy a dehydrator and place the cacao on it.^Then, place a the choco powder with any fruit or sweet thing you can think of, then wait two days.^After that, it's done.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailBundle3Done2": "A gift from Levi:",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailBundle4Done": "^Greetings, my dear @, for tis I, Camélia!^I am writing this on behalf of my dear, sweet husband, for he saw you leaving that old, abandoned house with a magic Pampering Machine!^So, may I guide you on how to create beautiful presents with it, yes?^First of all, to make this exotic machine work, you will need a gold bar and any crystal or mineral you can think of.^Place these beauties on the machine and wait for a week.^After that, you may gift, sell, or keep it to yourself!^Give it a try, I have an extra gold bar here.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailBundle4Done2": "A gift from Camélia:",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_JoseAndHisFamilyMovedInMail": "^Hello there, farmer! My name is José. Me and my family moved in to that old house you helped Mr. Levi refurnish.^It's a pleasure to meet you! Come visit us when you have the time!",
