    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisIntroduction.1": "I wonder what's beyond these stairs.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisIntroduction.2": "And who...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest1": "You're here!#$b#Good! I have an important task for you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest2": "Come on, follow me.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest3": "I saw you sneaking on that old building these days.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest4": "I saw in your face, the way you wanted to help.#$b#That gave me a flicker of hope...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest5": "Do you know what's beyond these stairs?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest6": "There's a village, a beautiful place called ''Harpy Town''.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest7": "The town was built not long ago, by immigrants from a country called Pindo-Rama.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest8": "They brought their own culture, festivals, food.#$b#I'm also from this country!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest9": "What should I say?...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest10": "Wait, really?! That's so cool!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest11": "I'm also from Pindo-Rama! I didn't know there was a community here!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest12": "Ahahah, it sure is!$1#$b#I bet you're gonna love the community!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest13": "Wait, really? Oh that's so cool! I bet you're gonna feel at home then!$1#$b#That's what I felt when I first arrived with...#$b#...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest14": "*Ahem*",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest15": "Anyways...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest16": "Pelican town also helped us to build our little community. We lived together in harmony for a while then. We were even able to sign a contract with Joja! $1#$b# Until...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest17": "After a storm, the only path leading to the town was blocked by debris...$2#$b#My friends have been stuck there since.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest18": "That's so sad, auntie.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest19": "I'm sorry for that, but what does this have to do with me?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest20": "Why don't you ask Joja to remove it?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest21": "Yes, sweetie, it sure is.$2#$b#But you can help remove these rocks, can't you?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest22": "Well, you have a pickaxe with you, don't you?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest23": "I did, they said they need the materials, but I don't have them.$2#$b#Guess it's up to you to remove it then.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest24": "Wait!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest25": "I was just joking! You're not going to make the manual work, just deliver the materials! It's not that hard$2#$b#Also, are you going to leave this poor old lady here? Alone?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest26": "Okay! Go, then! Just letting you know that I have a lot of money, I could pay you well!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest27": "*sigh* fine then...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest28": "Money?! Count me in!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest29": "Wait, really?!$1#$b#I mean, great! I'll go talk to Mr. Morris!#$b# I knew I could count on you!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest30": "Guess this is the beginning of a new adventure...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest31": "You weren't able to finish the commission in time!$2#$b#Why?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest32": "Lucky you I was able to talk to joja...#$b#They gave us one more season.$1#$b#Now... About your materials...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest33": "They have been confiscated by Joja...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest34": "They... WHAT?!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest35": "Don't worry, auntie, I didn't put any materials on the box.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest36": "I know, sweetheart, I know...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest37": "But hey...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest38": "Think about the bright side!#$b#Once you're done, you'll be recieving a great amount of money!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest39": "Oh, phew! You're safe, then!$1#$b#Wait a minute... You didn't even try?!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_THTstairsDebrisQuest40": "Hey! Come back here!",
