    //Cooking recipes
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailBebelRecipe": "Hey! I found this old recipe while cleaning my room. I believe it will be useful for you if you want to bake some sweets.^-Bebel",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_BebelRecipe": "Bebel's Recipe",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailCidaRecipe": "@! My dear trusted friend...^ This is my official sugarcane juice recipe. I want to share it with you to celebrate our wealth and success.^-Cida",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CidaRecipe": "Cida's Recipe",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailPrincessRecipe": "@!^ I was cleaning the house when, suddently, Princess came to me with a sheet of paper in her mouth. When I checked it, it was an old recipe of a candy I used to bake for my children. You can have it.^-Cida",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PrincessRecipe": "Princess's Recipe",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailAnahiRecipe": "Heeeeeeeeeeeeey, @!^ Since you're the super-duper-coolest-ever-farmer-I've-ever-seen, you can have my mega-hyper-coolest-greatest-Chimarrão-Recipe!^See ya later!^-Anahi",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AnahiRecipe": "Anahi's Recipe",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailMayaraRecipe": "How are you doing, Sweetpea?^ Have this little recipe I used to make with Raoni, when he wasn't sick.^It's very important to me, so take good care of it.^-Granny Mayara",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MayaraRecipe": "Mayara's Recipe",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailFranciscoRecipe": "Hey...^ Have this recipe, and NO QUESTIONS! Hmph!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FranciscoRecipe": "Francisco's Recipe",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailAdriannoRecipe": "Hello there, friend!^ Have this recipe. Me and my family used to make brigadeiros together when I was a kid, but we don't the time to do it anymore... Anyways, have it.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AdriannoRecipe": "Adrianno's Recipe",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailJuRecipe": "Sup, loser.^Found this old recipe on my drawer these days.^It's useless to me, have it.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_JuRecipe": "Julieta's Recipe",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailCameliaRecipe": "^Good morning, my dear friend, for tis I, Camélia, am sending the marvelous and exotic recipe I used to cook for Julieta when she was a kid.^Make sure, my dear friend, you shall cook this dish correctly, for a simple error might cause horrible consequences...^Farewell, my dear friend, I shall return to my humble residence now, have a wonderful day.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CameliaRecipe": "Camélia's Recipe",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MailLeviRecipe": "^Hiya, @!^ Have this, it's good.",
