    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fruit3SaplingDesc": "Takes 28 days to produce a mature Jatobá tree. Bears fruit in the Summer. Only grows if the 8 surrounding ''Tiles'' are empty.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fruit4": "Guava",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fruit4Desc": "So sweet and tasty!",
