    //Cida
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IntroductionCida": "Well, well, well... If it isn't the new farmer everyone is talking about...#$b# Welcome to our humble town, dear @! My name is Aparecida, but you can call me auntie Cida. I feel like we're going to be great friends!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_DumpsterDiveCommentCida": "How absurd! How disgusting! Get out of here!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRainCida": "%Cida is praying",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRainFinishedCida": "@! Thank Yoba you're okay!$2#$b# From what I've heard, this mysterious rain makes your hair fall out...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRain2Cida": "The mysterious rain is back! I've heard it's perfect for our capilar health!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HitBySlingshotCida": "Hey! You! What on earth you think you're doing?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortEnteringCida": "Ah! Finally a moment to relax from my chores!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortLeavingCida": "Time flies when we're resting...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortShoreCida": "*sigh* I'm getting older everyday... sometimes I wonder if I enjoyed life to the fullest.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortChairCida": "Hey @! You should sit down and relax a little!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortBarCida": "%Cida is drinking... a bit too much...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortUmbrellaCida": "I'll stay here for a while. The sun is too strong.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortTowelCida": "There's sand everywhere! Ugh! It's pissing me off!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortWanderCida": "Oh hey there! I'm just searching for inspiration for my new product!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortCida": "Wha- No! I'm not angry! It's just- I hate sand!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AcceptBirthdayGiftNegativeCida": "Princess can poop a better gift than... whatever the hell this is!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AcceptBirthdayGiftPositiveCida": "For... me? I... Don't even know what to say, @...$2#$b#Thank you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectBouquetCida": "I have no time for romance! I'm a busy woman!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectMermaidPendantCida": "I have no time for marriage! I'm a busy woman!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectRoommateProposalCida": "I would rather stay on my house, thank you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectMovieTicketCida": "I have no time for movies! I'm a busy woman!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairJudgingCida": "You should be glad I'm not participating, my products are million times better than whathever these are.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairJudgedCida": "Did you win?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LovedGiftCida": "Thank you, kid! You just made this old lady's day better!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LikedGiftCida": "How nice! Now leave me alone.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_NeutralGiftCida": "Thanks.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_DislikedGiftCida": "How... nice... Now, leave me alone.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HatedGiftCida": "Princess can poop a better gift than... whatever the hell this is!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MonCida": "Oh, hey! Need something?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Mon2Cida": "Did you know I'm the owner of a multi-million dollar company?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Mon4Cida": "Hey, @! Want some sugarcane juice?#$b#You'll have to pay for it, of course!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Mon6Cida": "Oh, hello...$2#$b#Sorry, I'm not feeling well today...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Mon8Cida": "I should've been a better mother to him...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Mon10Cida": "Hey, kiddo! Wanna chat a bit?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TueCida": "%Cida is ignoring you",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Tue2Cida": "Oh hey! Do you have any money? I need a few pennies for my business.#$b#I promise I'll pay you later.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Tue4Cida": "Ever tried running a business all by yourself? No? Then don't complain when I look tired.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Tue6Cida": "I had a dream about my old job last night...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Tue8Cida": "Oh, hello...$2#$b#Sorry, auntie is not feeling well today...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Tue10Cida": "I wish I had the chance to say sorry...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WedCida": "I'm very smart! I know how to speak two languages!$1#$b#...#$b#Aren't you... going to praise me for that?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Wed2Cida": "My name means ''Appears'' in my mother language.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Wed4Cida": "Oh, hey... sorry, I don't wanna talk...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Wed6Cida": "Princess barked at thin air today... Spirits, maybe? Dogs sense things, you know.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Wed8Cida": "Hey! Need something? I'm all ears.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Wed10Cida": "Hey, @. Have you seen my son somewhere?#$b#Can you give this to him?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ThuCida": "%Cida doesn't seem to notice you.#$b#I wish I was rich...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Thu2Cida": "Maybe one day I'll pay Serena the money I owe her. We'll see...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Thu4Cida": "Princess is my best friend!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Thu6Cida": "Princess is my best friend!$1#$b#I'm afraid of the day she'll not be here anymore...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Thu8Cida": "I owe Serena money...$2#$b#I wish I had the courage to pay her and say sorry...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Thu10Cida": "I'm sorry for lying to you, @...$2#$b#Auntie will try her best so that won't happen again!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FriCida": "What do you want? Can't you see I'm busy?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fri2Cida": "I don't understand Shane... How can someone not believe in Yoba?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fri4Cida": "I left everything behind to follow my dream as a successfull businesswoman, sometimes I wonder if it was worthy...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fri6Cida": "I left everything behind to follow my dream as a successfull businesswoman, sometimes I wonder if it was worthy...$2#$b#...$2#$b#Come to think of it, anything is better than that damn place I used to work on.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fri8Cida": "Oh, hey... No, it's nothing...$2#$b#%Cida is ignoring you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fri10Cida": "Even though I don't understand how can someone not believe in Yoba, it's their opinion and I shouldn't judge them for that.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SatCida": "%Cida is ignoring you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Sat2Cida": "No, I'm not ignoring you. Leave me alone.#$b#%Cida is ignoring you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Sat4Cida": "%Cida pinched your cheeks.#$b#Aren't you the sweetest thing in the world?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Sat6Cida": "Not now, dear. Auntie have things to do.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Sat8Cida": "*sigh* I wonder how I will pay Serena...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Sat10Cida": "No, I'm not ignoring you. Auntie just... needs more time for herself.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SunCida": "What do you want? Can't you see I'm busy?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Sun2Cida": "Hm? Where is my business located? Well, in front of my house!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Sun4Cida": "Oh, hey... sorry, I don't wanna talk...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Sun6Cida": "I tried a new recipe yesterday... and burned everything.$2#$b#Again.$2#$b#Hey! Don't laugh!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Sun8Cida": "Oh, hey... No, it's nothing...$2#$b#%Cida is ignoring you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Sun10Cida": "No, I'm not ignoring you. Auntie just... needs more time for herself.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring1Cida": "Ah! Spring! New year, new me!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMonCida": "%Cida is ignoring you",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon2Cida": "Did you know I'm the owner of a multi-million dollar company?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon4Cida": "Lilica used to buy plants that were almost dying. And she was able to save all of them somehow.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon6Cida": "The weather goes perfect for a sugarcane juice!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon8Cida": "Ignorance is Joja's greatest weapon... and Mayara's biggest headache.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon10Cida": "All my children's names starts with ''L''!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTueCida": "Oh, hey! Need something?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue2Cida": "How are you doing today, @?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue4Cida": "%Cida pinched your cheeks.#$b#Aren't you the sweetest thing in the world?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue6Cida": "I remember calling my son Leonardo, Leleo. He hated this nickname.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue8Cida": "%Cida seems sad today.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue10Cida": "You remind me of my daughther Lilica. She was also a farmer!$1#$b#I miss her so much...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWedCida": "I'm very smart! I know how to speak two languages!$1#$b#...#$b#Aren't you... going to praise me for that?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed2Cida": "My intuition says you're up to something...#$b#Don't worry, I like trouble when it's interesting! Come and tell me all the gossip later!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed4Cida": "I left everything behind to follow my dream as a successfull businesswoman, sometimes I wonder if it was worthy...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed6Cida": "I left everything behind to follow my dream as a successfull businesswoman, sometimes I wonder if it was worthy...$2#$b#...$2#$b#Come to think of it, anything is better than that damn place I used to work on.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed8Cida": "Haven't heard of Lilica since last year, I hope she's okay...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed10Cida": "You're always welcome here, @. My door is open, my coffee is warm, and my patience, well... it depends on the day!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThuCida": "*%Cida doesn't seem to notice you.#$b#*sigh* I wish I was rich...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu2Cida": "Leonardo, Lillia, Luna, Lana, Leandro, Laila, Lilica and Lucas. They're all my children!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu4Cida": "Lilica loved spring. I remember how colorful her garden was.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu6Cida": "I miss Leleo...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu8Cida": "Leonardo, Lillia, Luna, Lana, Leandro, Laila, Lilica and Lucas. They're all my children!$1#$b#I wish I was a better mother to them...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu10Cida": "Lilica loved spring. I remember how colorful her garden was.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFriCida": "Why won't I go to the saloon like everyone else? I'm a busy woman",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri2Cida": "%Cida is silent.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri4Cida": "You remind me of my daughther Lilica. She was also a farmer!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri6Cida": "Some days I pretend everything is fine... but it's not. I'm just tired, @.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri8Cida": "Lilica was a bit hard to deal with, but she's still my sweetheart!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri10Cida": "Why won't I go to the saloon like everyone else? Let's just say... I owe Gus a few pennies...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSatCida": "Isn't princess such a cute puppy?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat2Cida": "You can always pet Princess if you want! She loves it!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat4Cida": "From where I'm from, they don't sell fish tacos, and I never had the chance to eat it.#$b#But since I tried it on, I never grew tired of it.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat6Cida": "If you're here just to gossip... Perfect!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat8Cida": "I planted some herbs today. I hope I don't kill them this time.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat10Cida": "I've never had a husband. Relationships are too hard to maintain.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSunCida": "What do you want? Can't you see I'm busy?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun2Cida": "I see Princess likes you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun4Cida": "You think I could be a good mother?$2#$b#...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun6Cida": "Need something? Auntie is a bit busy right now.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun8Cida": "If you came to help me with chores, feel free. If not, well... you can still stay.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun10Cida": "Come here, sit, let's chat a bit!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer1Cida": "Summer... Ugh...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMonCida": "What do you want? Can't you see I'm busy?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon2Cida": "Did you know I'm the owner of a multi-million dollar company?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon4Cida": "Lilica used to buy plants that were almost dying. And she was able to save all of them somehow.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon6Cida": "My Saint Aparecidinha protects me from the evil from this world. I even have a small statue of Her on my room.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon8Cida": "I hate this weather...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon10Cida": "I hate this weather... Reminds me of Leleo...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTueCida": "The money I owe Gus? Oh, yeah, I'll pay him later.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue2Cida": "Ugh, this heat! Even my thoughts are sweating.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue4Cida": "I'm sweating... Ugh, disgusting...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue6Cida": "Lana used to say I was her 2nd mama. Her 1st mama was Aparecidinha. Isn't this cute?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue8Cida": "@! Don't forget to drink water!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue10Cida": "I've had 8 children in my life. Lucas is the youngest.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWedCida": "%Cida doesn't seem to notice you.#$b#*sigh* I wish I was rich...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed2Cida": "I remember my kid, Luna, hated summer.#$b#Wearing all those heavy clothes and crazy jewelry after all...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed4Cida": "This weather makes me sick.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed6Cida": "Laila's name come from the stars.$1#$b#I remember not knowing what to name her when she was born.#$b#Then, when I looked at the hospital window, I saw a beautiful star on the sky...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed8Cida": "I hate this weather...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed10Cida": "I hate this weather... Reminds me of Leleo...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThuCida": "Ugh... So hot today...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu2Cida": "What do you want? Yes, I'm angry because of the sun. It's too hot!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu4Cida": "Oh, hey... sorry, I don't wanna talk...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu6Cida": "Leleo loved to go to the beach.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu8Cida": "Oh Leleo, my son... I miss you...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu10Cida": "Year after year and I'm still here... rotting alone. I should win an award.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFriCida": "Isn't princess the cutest puppy in the world?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri2Cida": "This weather pisses me off.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri4Cida": "Sometimes I wonder if I should move somewhere colder. But then who would take care of Princess? She loves summer!$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri6Cida": "%Cida seems sad today.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri8Cida": "Can't wait for the summer to end.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri10Cida": "Don't forget your sunscreen, dear!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSatCida": "%Cida is ignoring you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat2Cida": "This weather pisses me off.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat4Cida": "%Cida pinched your cheeks.#$b#Aren't you the sweetest thing in the world?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat6Cida": "Years ago, Serena told me to ''face my responsibilities''. I told her I'm trying! Slowly.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat8Cida": "Leonardo loved his name so much, he gave his son the same name!$1#$b#I miss my son...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat10Cida": "@! It's hot outside! Have this![{{ModId}}_SugarCaneJuice]",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSunCida": "I'm very smart! I know how to speak two languages!$1#$b#...#$b#Aren't you... going to praise me for that?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun2Cida": "Princess tried to bite Sebastian as he was riding his bike yesterday.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun4Cida": "Have you eaten today, @? Then go eat something RIGHT NOW! I don't want to see you faint at my doorstep.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun6Cida": "I'm not nosy, I'm just... Well, curious to know the truth, eheheheh!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun8Cida": "How I met princess? I found her on a dark alley while she was just a small puppy.#$b#All hurt and dirty, poor girl...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun10Cida": "I've had 8 children in my life. Lucas is the youngest.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall1Cida": "Fall is my favorite season. The world finally matches my mood.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMonCida": "%Cida is ignoring you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon2Cida": "Did you know I'm the owner of a multi-million dollar company?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon4Cida": "Lilica used to buy plants that were almost dying. And she was able to save all of them somehow.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon6Cida": "Lana used to say I was her 2nd mama. Her 1st mama was Aparecidinha. Isn't this cute?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon8Cida": "I miss Lana, my baby...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon10Cida": "Lana left this world too soon...$2#$b#Sometimes I wonder how life would be if my little girl was here...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTueCida": "Maybe one day I'll pay Gus...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue2Cida": "Princess and Pam are my best friends.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue4Cida": "Back home, people used to say I talked too much. Can you believe that?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue6Cida": "%Cida seems sad today.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue8Cida": "Oh, hey... No, it's nothing...$2#$b#%Cida is ignoring you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue10Cida": "%Cida doesn't want to talk right now.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWedCida": "Hey, did you know I'm rich?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed2Cida": "Hey, did you know I have a lot of money?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed4Cida": "If I were you, I'd take a break. But I'm not you, right? So go, keep overworking yourself anyway.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed6Cida": "Leonardo, Lillia, Luna, Lana, Leandro, Laila, Lilica and Lucas. They're all my children!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed8Cida": "Leonardo, Lillia, Luna, Lana, Leandro, Laila, Lilica and Lucas. They're all my children!$1#$b#I wish I was a better mother to them...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed10Cida": "Fall was Lucas's favourite season...#$b#...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThuCida": "Maybe one day I'll pay Pierre...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu2Cida": "%Cida is ignoring you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu4Cida": "%Cida pinched your cheeks.#$b#Aren't you the sweetest thing in the world?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu6Cida": "I'm not nosy, I'm just curious to know the truth, eheheheh!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu8Cida": "Hey, @! Take care of yourself!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu10Cida": "You're always welcome here, @. My door is open, my coffee is warm, and my patience, well... it depends on the day!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFriCida": "%Cida is ignoring you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri2Cida": "The money I owe Pierre? Oh, yeah, I'll pay him later.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri4Cida": "%Cida doesn't seem to notice you.#$b#If I ever get rich, I'll buy a mansion bigger than Mayor Lewis' ego! Eheheheheh...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri6Cida": "I hope Lucas is okay in this cold...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri8Cida": "If you ever need advice, come to me. Auntie Cida knows everything. Or pretends to.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri10Cida": "Joja always make sure Mayara is too busy to notice them taking advantage of the valley.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSatCida": "What do you want?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat2Cida": "I've had 8 children, and none of them dare to visit me...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat4Cida": "Oh, hey... sorry, I don't wanna talk...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat6Cida": "I'm sorry, I'm feeling a bit sad today...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat8Cida": "I've had 8 children, and none of them dare to visit me...$2#$b#But sometimes I realize how much I neglected them...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat10Cida": "I wish I had the chance to say sorry to all of them...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSunCida": "Hey! How are you doing today?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun2Cida": "Maybe one day I'll pay Pierre...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun4Cida": "Fall is beautiful, don't you think?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun6Cida": "You bring a good energy, you know? This valley needed that.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun8Cida": "Leonardo loved his name so much, he gave his son the same name!$1#$b#I miss my son...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun10Cida": "Oh, you... wanna know what happened to Leonardo?$2#$b#...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter1Cida": "Winter always brings old memories... some warm, some painful.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMonCida": "Hey! Aren't you cold?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon2Cida": "Did you know I'm the owner of a multi-million dollar company?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon4Cida": "%Cida pinched your cheeks.#$b#Aren't you the sweetest thing in the world?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon6Cida": "I miss the old times...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon8Cida": "Everyday I ask my Saint Aparecidinha to protect my children.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon10Cida": "Everyday I ask my Saint Aparecidinha to protect my children.$1#$b#Specially Leandro... I'm so worried about him...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTueCida": "Need something?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue2Cida": "The money I owe Pierre? Oh, yeah, I'll pay him later.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue4Cida": "Cold mornings remind me of home... How bad I felt on my old job... And why I left.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue6Cida": "Money isn't everything... but it does help you sleep better, you know?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue8Cida": "Hey! How are you doing?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue10Cida": "I've had 8 children in my life. Lucas is the youngest.#$b#I can consider you my 9th!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWedCida": "Maybe one day I'll pay Robin...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed2Cida": "Laila hated winter. And honestly, I agree with her.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed4Cida": "Lilica used to buy plants that were almost dying. And she was able to save all of them somehow.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed6Cida": "I'm not nosy, I'm just curious to know the truth, eheheheh!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed8Cida": "*sigh* I miss Leleo...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed10Cida": "Leandro lived with Luna, they both have that gender thing.#$b#Like, he was born a girl, but then he... he... what's the word again?... transitionated?...#$b#I don't know how to explain, sorry... The only thing I know, is that he's a man.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThuCida": "Luna gets on my nerves sometimes...$3#$b#Last time we talked to eachother, he... she... well, they told me they're neither a boy, nor a girl...$2#$b#I don't understand...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu2Cida": "Maybe one day I'll pay Pierre...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu4Cida": "Pam is one of my only friends in the town. We're gossip buddies!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu6Cida": "Princess bit Sam yesterday.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu8Cida": "Now I understand what Luna, my child, meant$2#$b#I wish I was more supportive that time...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu10Cida": "Luna was a kind kid. With a sweet voice and a good heart. i wish I could talk to them again...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFriCida": "Oh, Hey! Need something?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri2Cida": "Oh, hey! Say hi to Pam for me.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri4Cida": "%Cida pinched your cheeks.#$b#Aren't you the sweetest thing in the world?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri6Cida": "Lana used to say I was her 2nd mama. Her 1st mama was Aparecidinha. Isn't this cute?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri8Cida": "Lillia moved to Zuzu City years ago... Have you met her? She works for Joja!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri10Cida": "Don't push yourelf too much, dear.#$b#Don't you dare leave auntie Cida worried!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSatCida": "Money is everything to me!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat2Cida": "Need something?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat4Cida": "Princess woke me up at 3 AM barking at a bush. I'm exhausted.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat6Cida": "Money isn't everything... but it does help you sleep better, you know?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat8Cida": "Hey! How are you doing?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat10Cida": "Hello, @! How are you doing today?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSunCida": "Maybe one day I'll pay Serena...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun2Cida": "What do you want? I'm busy...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun4Cida": "My joints hurt so much today... Getting old sucks.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun6Cida": "%Cida seems sad today.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun8Cida": "Sit with me for a moment, @. Silence feels lighter when you're not alone.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun10Cida": "@! Come in! Have a cup of warm tea, it's cold outside![614]",
