    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon2Bebel": "I have an auntie, Vitória, maybe one day you get the chance to meet her and Michelly!#$b#Mm? Who's Michelly? Her motorcycle!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon4Bebel": "Auntie Vitória ran away after she lost the elections, I wonder why...$2#$b#She's not the type to accept defeat... Weird.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon6Bebel": "I miss auntie Vitória chatting about Michelly, her motorcycle.$2#$b#Wonder if one day she'll come back...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon8Bebel": "I'm sorry, just thinking about my auntie...$2#$b#She's not the type to succumb to humilliation... There's something wrong...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon10Bebel": "My auntie always said that, one day, I would find my true love.$1#$b#And there you are!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTueBebel": "Let's hope this wind won't ruin my hair...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue2Bebel": "Let's hope this wind won't ruin my hair...$2#$b#Oh, hey @! How are you?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue4Bebel": "Let's hope this wind won't ruin my hair...$2#$b#Oh, hey @! Windy day today, isn't it?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue6Bebel": "Let's hope this wind won't ruin my hair...$2#$b#Oh, hey @! Windy day today, isn't it? Be careful not to catch a cold!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue8Bebel": "Let's hope this wind won't ruin my hair...$2#$b#Oh, hey @! Windy day today, isn't it? A perfect day for a tea party!$1#$b#And you're totally invited, eheheheh~...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue10Bebel": "Let's hope this wind won't ruin my hair...$2#$b#Oh, hey @! Windy day today, isn't it? A perfect day for a romantic date, am I right?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWedBebel": "I'm planning to have a picnic with my friends, but I've been so busy these days I keep forgeting it...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed2Bebel": "I'm planning to have a picnic with my friends, but I've been so busy these days I keep forgeting it...$2#$b#You can come too, I guess...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed4Bebel": "I'm planning to have a picnic with my friends, but I've been so busy these days I keep forgeting it...$2#$b#Hey, wanna come too?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed6Bebel": "I'm planning to have a tea party with my friends and their dolls, but I've been so busy these days I keep forgeting it...$2#$b#Hey, you can come too if you want!$1#$b#Do you have any dolls?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed8Bebel": "Just planned a tea party with my friends and their dolls!$2#$b#Hey, you can come too if you want!$1#$b#Do you have any dolls?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed10Bebel": "Hey, wanna go out on a tea-party-date?$1#$b#Why? Oh, so we can relax, eat some snacks...$1#$b#We can also be alone for a bit...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThuBebel": "Harpy Town's radio is so boring, Joja only selects boring songs...$2#$b#Sometimes I wonder why can't we choose the musics...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu2Bebel": "Sometimes I wonder if that contract auntie Vitória made with Joja was worthy...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu4Bebel": "I love Cipó Buarque, I sent millions of emails for Joja to add it on the radio, but they never did...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu6Bebel": "I've had enough! I'll listen to what I like! Not what Joja wants!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu8Bebel": "Hey, wanna relax a little? You're always welcome at my home!$1#$b#I also have some old music CDs if you want to dance a little!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu10Bebel": "Hey, umm... Wanna dance slowly at the sound of Rita Lima?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFriBebel": "I saw your farm from afar while walking to Pelican Town.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri2Bebel": "I saw your farm from afar while walking to Pelican Town.#$b#Think you're doing nice!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri4Bebel": "I saw your farm from afar while walking to Pelican Town.#$b#It's beautiful! Hope you're doing okay!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri6Bebel": "I saw your farm from afar while walking to Pelican Town.#$b#It's beautiful! Hope you're doing okay!$1#$b#Oh and if you need any help, don't hesitate to call me!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri8Bebel": "I saw your farm from afar while walking to Pelican Town.#$b#It's beautiful! I think you're doing so good!$1#$b#Oh and if you need any help, don't hesitate to call me!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri10Bebel": "I saw your farm from afar while walking to Pelican Town.#$b#It's beautiful! your job is amazing!$1#$b#Can I come over and spend some time with you one day?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSatBebel": "The leaves are so beautiful this year...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat2Bebel": "The leaves are so beautiful this year... Don't you think?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat4Bebel": "I love to sit and watch the leaves fall on the ground...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat6Bebel": "I love to sit and watch the leaves fall on the ground...#$b#It's so poetic, I don't know why.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat8Bebel": "Have you ever wondered how anything our eyes capture in our life can be turned into a beautiful painting?#$b#Heheheh... Just feeling inspired today...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat10Bebel": "Have you ever wondered how anything our eyes capture in our life can be turned into a beautiful painting?#$b#Heheheh... I wish I was good at painting, so I could draw you...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSunBebel": "Hey, @! How are you doing today?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun2Bebel": "Hey, @! Are you okay? careful not to catch a cold in this weather!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun4Bebel": "Harpy town's climate is, somehow, warmer than Pelican town's. Weird.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun6Bebel": "Harpy town's climate is, somehow, warmer than Pelican town's. Weird.$2#$b#Maybe it's an inexplicable and mystical phenomenon.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun8Bebel": "I've been feeling more at home in Harpy town. I believe that's a good thing, isn't it?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun10Bebel": "I feel at home wherever you're around me...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter1Bebel": "Ah! I love winter$1#$b#Mm? The reason I love every season?#$b#Oh! It's because I think that, just like flowers, each one has its unique beauty!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMonBebel": "Ugh... Working in this cold should be illegal...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon2Bebel": "Ugh... Waking up early in this cold should be illegal...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon4Bebel": "I wish I could lay on my bed and stay under the warm blankets all day.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon6Bebel": "Papa used to say that I dress like an old lady for winter.$2#$b#I wonder if it's true, how embarrassing...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon8Bebel": "Papa used to say that I dress like an old lady for winter.$1#$b#Well, it's not my fault that old ladies have such a cool taste for fashion.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon10Bebel": "Hi, @, dear! It's good to see you!$1#$b#How do I look?$4#$b#%Bebel spinned aroud happily.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTueBebel": "It's so hard to walk on the snow with those heels.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue2Bebel": "It's so hard to walk on the snow with those heels.$2#$b#Oh hey, @! Aren't you cold?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue4Bebel": "It's not weird to change your dolls clothes to warmer ones at winter so they won't catch a cold, isn't it?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue6Bebel": "I always make sure to change my doll's clothes to warmer ones, so they won't catch a cold!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue8Bebel": "Hey, wanna play dress up? Do you have a doll?$1#$b#I have plenty of mini clothes on my house! I knit them myself!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue10Bebel": "@!#$b#Bebel kissed you on the cheek, leaving a lipstick mark on your face.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWedBebel": "I think I'll need to wear glasses...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed2Bebel": "I think I'll need to wear glasses...$2#$b#Bet I'll look like an old lady.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed4Bebel": "The PCs at Joja's are TERRIBLE! Ugh! They are slow and filled with viruses! It drives me crazy!!!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed6Bebel": "Hey, @! You look radiant today!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed8Bebel": "I feel so beautiful and feminine today!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed10Bebel": "Babe, do you think about my dolls as our children? Because I do!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThuBebel": "So cold...$2#$b#Oh, hi! Need something?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu2Bebel": "So cold...$2#$b#Oh, hi! Take care of yourself!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu4Bebel": "@! Aren't you cold?$3#$b#Take care of yourself, okay?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu6Bebel": "@! Aren't you cold?$3#$b#Take care of yourself, okay? I'm worried about you...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu8Bebel": "@! Good you're here! It's so cold!$3#$b#Make sure to take care of yourself, okay?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu10Bebel": "%Bebel gave you a warm hug#$b#I wish I could stay on this hug forever...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFriBebel": "Julieta said I look like an old lady in this dress... Ugh! She pisses me off sometimes!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri2Bebel": "Julieta said I look like an old lady in this dress... Ugh! She knows nothing about fashion!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri4Bebel": "Hey, do you think I look like an old lady with this dress?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri6Bebel": "Paçoca offers so much support to Raoni, it's beautiful to see!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri8Bebel": "I don't care about what Juju says, I'm beautiful, I'm stylish, I'm looking like a fashionable old lady!$1#$b#The coolest grandma on the neighborhood!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri10Bebel": "I love the way you dress, my love!$1#$b#I think we're the most fashionable couple at the town!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSatBebel": "The snow is so pretty!$1#$b#From where I came from, it doesn't snow.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat2Bebel": "The snow is so pretty!$1#$b#From where I came from, it doesn't snow.#$b#Oh hey, @! Didn't see you coming!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat4Bebel": "The snow is so pretty!$1#$b#From where I came from, it doesn't snow.#$b#Oh hey, @! Let's build a snowman!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat6Bebel": "The snow always amazed me... It's so pretty and soft!$1#$b#Oh hey, @! Didn't see you coming!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat8Bebel": "The snow always amazed me... It's so pretty and soft!$1#$b#Oh hey, @! Let's build a snowman!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat10Bebel": "%Bebel threw a snowball at you.#$b#C'mon, babe, let's play!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSunBebel": "Sunday is already depressing, now with winter...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun2Bebel": "Sunday is already depressing, now with winter...$2#$b#Cold seems to make things worse...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun4Bebel": "Gus told me Cida still owes him that money...$2#$b#Ugh! She drives me crazy!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun6Bebel": "Gus told me Cida still owes him that money...$2#$b#Guess I'll go talk to her... Again...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun8Bebel": "Thank you for never judging my hobbies, it means a lot to me!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun10Bebel": "@! You're here!$1#$b#Thank Yoba! Sundays for me are always depressing... But you brighten my day!#$b#So, how's your farm doing?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring12Bebel": "I think the egg hunt is for everyone, regardless of age!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring23Bebel": "I wonder if someone will ask me to dance, eheheheh...$4#$b#@! Oh dear Yoba! I didn't see you coming!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer10Bebel": "I don't trust that soup... What if someone poison it?!$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer27Bebel": "Walking in the sand at night with those heels is always a challenge for me...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall15Bebel": "@! Did you prepare yourself for the fair?$1#$b#I'll be cheering up for you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall26Bebel": "Spirit's eve is not a common tradition from where I came from, but I think it's fun!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter7Bebel": "I don't understand this tradition... What's so fun about fishing?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter24Bebel": "@! Don't forget my gift! Eheheheh, just kidding!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring12Y2Bebel": "I think the egg hunt is for everyone, regardless of age!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring23Y2Bebel": "I wonder if someone will ask me to dance, eheheheh...$4#$b#@! Oh dear Yoba! I didn't see you coming!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer10Y2Bebel": "I don't trust that soup... What if someone poison it?!$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer27Y2Bebel": "Walking in the sand at night with those heels is always a challenge for me...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall15Y2Bebel": "@! Did you prepare yourself for the fair?$1#$b#Bet you're going to win!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall26Y2Bebel": "Spirit's eve is not a common tradition from where I came from, but I think it's fun!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter7Y2Bebel": "I don't understand this tradition... What's so fun about fishing?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter24Y2Bebel": "@! Don't forget my gift! Eheheheh, just kidding!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MarriedToAnahiBebel": "Awwwwwwww you and Anahi are so cute together!$1#$b#Better prepare yourself, cause you'll be hearing fresh gossips everyday.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_cropMaturedMelonBebel": "I saw your farm from afar days ago... Your crops sure look healthy! Specially your melons.#$b#They're perfect for a pink cake.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_BebelGTinteraction1": "%Bebel picked up the doll, nesting it on her arms and not minding the dirt on her clothes.#$b#My, look at you... Don't worry, mama's going to take good care of you...$2#$b#Oh! Um... I mean, thank you, @!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_BebelGTinteraction2": "Oh thank you, @! I've been looking for this book, like, everywhere!$1#$b#Now I can fullfill my duties faster!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_BebelGTinteraction3": "Oooooh! Is that a pink cake I see?$1#$b#H-huh?! It's for... Me?!$3#$b#Awwwww, @, stop it , you!... I'm flattered, thanks!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_BebelGTinteraction1R": "Sorry, @, but I can't eat nor drink anything with milk...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EventSeenBebel1": "Once again, @, thank you... For everything you've done to us.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RSVjuneBebel": "Waaaaaah... Isn't June so... Dreamy?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RSVprankBebel": "I'm sorry, @, but you smell terrible...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RSVjuneBebel2": "Hey, @, let's visit the log cabin one day!$1#$b#We can dance in slow motion at the sound of the piano...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RSVprankBebel2": "I'm sorry, @, my love, but you smell terrible...$2",
    //Marriage dialogue
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EngagementBebel1": "I can't believe I'm finally getting married!$4#$b#@... You make me feel like a princess...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EngagementBebel2": "I can't wait to move to your farm, dear!$1#$b#We're going to live happily ever after!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDspringBebel": "This weather totally goes for a picnic!$1#$b#Don't you agree, my love?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDsummerBebel": "Whoa... It's getting hot in here!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDfallBebel": "Ah! Fall... Perfect weather for a tea party!$1#$b#Would you mind staying with your wife for a bit and have a cup of coffee?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDwinterBebel": "This weather is perfect for cuddling together... Isn't it, my love?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PatioBebel": "Good morning, sweetheart! I'm doing some important stuff at the moment! I'll be back in a bit!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay0Bebel": "You can take my umbrella with you, dear!$1#$b#Hope you don't mind it's all purple and pink with glitter!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay1Bebel": "Hey! Let's watch a movie together!#$b#A horror movie! If I get scared, I can just jump into your arms!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay2Bebel": "Careful not to catch a flu, sweetheart!$2#$b#If you do, I'll be here to take care of you!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay3Bebel": "Let's play dolls today, sweetheart!$1#$b#I'll be Ms. Flora and you'll be Mrs. Giraffe.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay4Bebel": "This weather goes for a tea party!$1#$b#Just me and you...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay5Bebel": "I should invite Anahi to gossip any time soon.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay0Bebel": "Good morning, sunshine! Have some cake![221]$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay1Bebel": "Make sure to rest when needed, my love!$1#$b#I would hate to see you all tired and sick...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay2Bebel": "Your kitchen is so big! I can cook tons of Pink Cakes here!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay3Bebel": "I woke up from a nightmare in the middle of the night yesterday...$2#$b#Luckly, I had you by my side...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay4Bebel": "Good morning!$1#$b#%Bebel kissed your cheek, leaving a lipstick mark behind.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay5Bebel": "Careful out there, my sweetheart! I always get worried about you...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight0Bebel": "This weather makes me depressed...$2#$b#I'm glad you're here for me, though!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight1Bebel": "The frogs are singing outside... I wonder if they feel cold...$2#$b#W-wait don't you even think about bringing one here!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight2Bebel": "Hey my love! Busy day? Let's relax a little, shall we?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight3Bebel": "You're home!$1#$b#Let's cuddle under the blankets.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight4Bebel": "Oh dear Yoba! You are all soaked!$3#$b#Let me take care of you, my love!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight5Bebel": "I love the sound of rain! Helps me sleep better...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight0Bebel": "My love! Do you want me to prepare a bubble bath for you before we go to sleep?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight1Bebel": "It's always nice to relax the muscles after a tiring day of work.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight2Bebel": "Oh dear Yoba... I'm so tired, I need to take a bath.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight3Bebel": "Want me to read a book for you and sing you to sleep? Eheheh just kidding!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight4Bebel": "Oh dear... You look tired!$2#$b#Don't worry, I'll take good care of you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight5Bebel": "Ouch! My back hurts...$2#$b#Hey! Um... Would you mind giving me a massage?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FunLeaveBebel": "I have some important things to do today, sweetheart. I'll be back at night!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FunReturnBebel": "My love! I missed you!$1#$b#%Bebel jumped into your arms, kissing your cheek and leaving a lipstick mark behind.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OutdoorBebel": "I love to go outside and breathe some frash air!$1#$b#Care to join me for a little?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor0Bebel": "I love to watch the sunrise from your farm!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor1Bebel": "I love our little farm! But maybe it will look better with more flowers...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor2Bebel": "Hey, do you think dolls can hear us?#$b#Because I do!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor3Bebel": "Your farm is so beautiful, my love! It totally represents your personality.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor4Bebel": "O dear knight... You saved me from the dragon! My heart is all yours... Let's live happily ever after in our castle!$4#$b#Mm? Who's the dragon?#$b#Well... Joja, of course!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SRBebel": "%Bebel is playing with her dolls.#$b#My my... Ms. Elizabeth how could you say such thing?!$3#$b#%Bebel shook the other doll, simulating her speaking. ''I said what I said! Robert is a liar! A traitor!'' She said in a high pitched voice.#$b#",
