    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri10Anahi": "Hey @! Wanna drink chimarrão and eat pizza with me later?$6#$b#A weird combination, I know... Just like us!$4#$b#A farmer and a journalist... I never thought...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSatAnahi": "Hey! Any gossips to tell me?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat2Anahi": "Oh I didn't noticed you there, how are you doing, @? I'm doing great by the way. Yeah that's it, bye!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat4Anahi": "Hi @! I'm running out of ideias for the news...$8#$b# If you have any suggestion or gossips can you, please, send me later?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat6Anahi": "Hey! It's the perfect season to drink some nice, cold chimarrão, have you tried yet?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat8Anahi": "Oh hey, @! This is the perfect timing for a chimarrão!!$3#$b#I like to drink it cold, how about you?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat10Anahi": "Oh hey, @, my boo! This is the perfect timing for a chimarrão$6#$b# Want to share one with me? It's cold I hope you don't mind.$6#$b#We can also put those heart-shaped straws they have in movies if you want...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSunAnahi": "Oh hey, @! Did you already checked my blog?$3#$b#I will never lose the opportunity to share my work with others!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun2Anahi": "Hey, @! Are you anxious for Fall? It's spooky season!#$b#I feel like it will be a great season for my news.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun4Anahi": "Mmmmmm... Oh hey, @!If you don't mind... can I interview you later?$3#$b#It's for my blog!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun6Anahi": "*Sigh* I ran out of ideias for the news...$8#$b# Oh hey, @! Quick, please help me with ideias for my blog, any gossips will do it.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun8Anahi": "Hmmmmmm... Oh hey, @!If you don't mind can I interview you later?$3#$b# I need to improve on my interviews and also it will be cool for the news!$1#$b#Imagine what the others will say... ''The great journalist Anahi interviewed the fantastic farmer @.''$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun10Anahi": "Hey, honey! Want to come to my place and drink some chimarrão?$6#$b#I like to drink it cold but at this point I guess you already know, heh...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall1Anahi": "I have mixed feelings for Fall. It's the season of my birthday, but also... Ugh! Pumpkins...$2",
