    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon10Anahi": "Boo! Did you know that you're the most fashionable person I know?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTueAnahi": "Haley always has some fresh gossips to share!$1#$b#Wha- No! I'm not telling you!$5#$b#It's personal...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue2Anahi": "Haley always has some fresh gossips to share!$1#$b#What? Oh... Sorry, but I can't tell you, it's personal...$2",
