    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSatAnahi": "No, I don't have ''pumpkinphobia''... I just find pumpkins smelly and disgusting...$5#$b#Hmph... Pumpkinphobia... This word doesn't even exist!$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat2Anahi": "No, I don't have ''pumpkinphobia''... I just find pumpkins smelly and disgusting...$5#$b#Hmph... Pumpkinphobia... This word doesn't even exist!$2#$b#Where did you take that word from?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat4Anahi": "I'm lucky granny doesn't care about me hating pumpkins.$3",
