    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat8Anahi": "Hey, I'm sorry if I sounded too nosy the first time we met...$8#$b#It's just... You looked cool and... And...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat10Anahi": "I would eat a whole pumpkin if that meant staying by your side forever...$4",
