    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun4Anahi": "Mama used to make pumpkin candies at sundays.$3#$b#I hated it...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun6Anahi": "Mama used to make pumpkin candies at sundays.$3#$b#She did that for years, I was even able to memorize the recipe.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun8Anahi": "Mama used to make pumpkin candies at sundays.$3#$b#She did that for years, I was even able to memorize the recipe.#$b#Yeah, I know it's a cool thing to publish on my blog, but the less people eating pumpkin, the better.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun10Anahi": "Hey, boo! How are you doing today?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter1Anahi": "Bye bye, Fall... Bye bye, pumpkins... Hello, winter!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMonAnahi": "I love to tell stories on winter!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon2Anahi": "I love to tell stories on winter!$1#$b#Hey, @! Maybe one day I'll tell you one!$1#$b#Juju often says my stories are boring...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon4Anahi": "I love to tell stories on winter!$1#$b#Do you know about the story of the Queimada Grande Island?#$b#It is also known as ''Snake Island'' and is not advised to go there, due the large amount of snakes that live in that region$3#$b#One of the species are Jararaca-Ilhoa, Bothrops insularis, a poisonous snake that can easily kill you.$3#$b#Neat, isn't it?!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon6Anahi": "Hey, @! Care to hear a story?#$b#Do you know about the story of the Queimada Grande Island?#$b#It is also known as ''Snake Island'' and is not advised to go there, due the large amount of snakes that live in that region$3#$b#One of the species are Jararaca-Ilhoa, Bothrops insularis, a poisonous snake that can easily kill you.$3#$b#Neat, isn't it?!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon8Anahi": "Hey, @! How are you doing? Nice weather today, isn't it? Perfect for a story!$1#$b#Do you know about the story of the brigadeiro? Yes, the little candy!$3#$b#It was a candy created in 1945 for a presidential campaign of the brigadeiro Eduardo Gomes!#$b#Yes, he was a brigadeiro, no, he wasn't a candy, being a brigadeiro means you work for the Pindó-Rama's air force.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon10Anahi": "Boo! Care to hear a story?$6#$b#Do you know about the story of the brigadeiro? Yes, the little candy!$3#$b#It was a candy created in 1945 for a presidential campaign of the brigadeiro Eduardo Gomes!#$b#Yes, he was a brigadeiro, no, he wasn't a candy, being a brigadeiro means you work for the Pindó-Rama's air force.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTueAnahi": "Juju keeps saying that Bebel looks like an old lady...$2#$b#I think Bebel is pretty good fashioned tho...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue2Anahi": "I should interview Bebel on her fashion choices!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue4Anahi": "I should interview Bebel on her fashion choices!$1#$b#Maybe this will make Juju shut up...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue6Anahi": "Juju is... not an easy person to deal with...$2#$b#Have you seen the way she talks to her dad?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue8Anahi": "Juju is... not an easy person to deal with...$2#$b#Have you seen the way she talks to her dad?$2#$b#*Sigh* Maybe I just don't know what she have been through...$2",
