    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu8Anahi": "I know spirit's eve is only in fall, but I think this weather is perfect for a horror story!$1#$b#Hey, care to hear one?$3#$b#The curse of Fofinho. It is said that the Fofinho doll contains a dark dagger inside of him... Which fixes his head with his body.$3#$b#Some says it's just to fix his head with his body, but others says that the doll is possessed, and that he whispers devilish things to children at night, so the kid could kill their parents with the dagger.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu10Anahi": "If kisses were snowflakes, I'd send you a blizzard.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFriAnahi": "I would totally go for a pizza right now.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri2Anahi": "I would totally go for a pizza right now.#$b#Mmmmmmm... Just imagine that delicious cheese melting...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri4Anahi": "Hey, @! Do you like horror stories? I have one here! I can tell you later if you want!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri6Anahi": "Hey, @! Do you like horror stories? I have one here!#$b#There's a story that, when someone have seven children, the eighth will be a werewolf.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri8Anahi": "Hey, @! Do you like horror stories? I have one here!#$b#Do you know about the story of the Dried-Body?#$b#He was a mean man that did so many bad things while living, that when he died, he was rejected by Yoba, the Devil and even the Earth itself, thus being forced to get out of his grave and roam on his dried-corpse.#$b#Scary, isn't it?!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri10Anahi": "I must be a snowflake... Because I've fallen for you.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSatAnahi": "Even though it's winter, I still drink my chimarrão cold!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat2Anahi": "@! Fun fact time$1#$b#Did you know that, in Pindó-Rama, there's a total of 6 biomes? These are Amazonia, Cerrado, Caatinga, Mata Atlântica, Pantanal and Pampa!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat4Anahi": "@! Fun fact time$1#$b#Did you know that, in Pindó-Rama, there's a total of 6 biomes? These are Amazonia, Cerrado, Caatinga, Mata Atlântica, Pantanal and Pampa!$3#$b#Neat, isn't it!?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat6Anahi": "@! Story time$1#$b#Do you know about the urban legend of the Blonde Ghost Girl?#$b#One version of the stories people tell is that, years ago, there was a beautiful blonde woman that was killed by a taxist#$b#Months later, another woman appeared on the road, she wore a black coat covering her face. She asked him to leave her next to the cemetery.#$b#When they arrived, she said ''You can leave me here, my house is a decent grave.'' And showed her face. It was the same woman the man killed months ago.#$b#He, then, died of a heart attack.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat8Anahi": "@! Story time$1#$b#Do you know about the urban legend of the Blonde Girl from the bathroom?#$b#One version of the stories people tell is that she appears to kids who skip classes on the bathroom, wearing cottons on her nose, and a long white dress.$3#$b#Others tell that you can invoke her by saying ''Loira do Banheiro'' three times in front of a mirror, then flush the toile three times and shout three swear words.$3#$b#Yeah, she's a Pindó-Rama version of Bloody Mary!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat10Anahi": "Boo! Story time$6#$b#Do you know about the urban legend of the Blonde Girl from the bathroom?#$b#One version of the stories people tell is that she appears to kids who skip classes on the bathroom, wearing cottons on her nose, and a long white dress.$3#$b#Others tell that you can invoke her by saying ''Loira do Banheiro'' three times in front of a mirror, then flush the toile three times and shout three swear words.$3#$b#Yeah, she's a Pindó-Rama version of Bloody Mary!$1",
