    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay0Anahi": "It's so interesting to watch the raindrops fall on the ground...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay1Anahi": "This weather is perfect to cuddle...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay2Anahi": "Boo! Careful not to catch a flu!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay3Anahi": "I think I saw a rainbow while looking out the window!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay4Anahi": "Wooooaaaaah! Rain! Time for a creepy story!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay5Anahi": "I'll post on my blog about us... The coolest couple in Pelican Town!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay0Anahi": "Boo! I... Think I burned the pizza... [382]$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay1Anahi": "Why don't you stay with me today?$6#$b#I can do whathever you want...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay2Anahi": "Boo! I love your sense of fashion, and... And your furniture... And... And... And you! And... Oh dear Yoba... I'm so in love with you...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay3Anahi": "You're so charming! Can you give me beauty suggestions so I can post them on my blog?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay4Anahi": "... I love you...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay5Anahi": "We should match bracelets!#$b#A best-friends-forever one, and a lovers ove...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight0Anahi": "Boo! Wanna watch a silly horror movie with me?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight1Anahi": "Rainy nights like this are perfect to tell horror stories!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight2Anahi": "Let's just relax and hear the raindrops falling on the ground.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight3Anahi": "Ah! The smell of rain is truly revigorating!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight4Anahi": "You're all soaked! Let me help you.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight5Anahi": "Mmmm... Maybe the rain will give me inspiration for my blog.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight0Anahi": "... Let's cuddle a bit.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight1Anahi": "Pelican town is usually so dark at night... It's scary...#$b#I'm lucky you're here to protect me tho...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight2Anahi": "It's a bit cold today, isn't it?#$b#Wanna cuddle a bit?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight3Anahi": "Why do painters always fall for their models?#$b#Because they love them with all of their art.$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight4Anahi": "Wooooah! I'm so tired! Just finished cleaning the whole house! I wanna take a bath!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight5Anahi": "Come here... I have a surprise for you...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FunLeaveAnahi": "Hey! I need to do some things today! I'll be back later!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FunReturnAnahi": "Heeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeey! Missed you!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OutdoorAnahi": "Woooooaaaaaaaah I think I just saw an UFO!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor0Anahi": "It's so beautiful to watch the sunrise here...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor1Anahi": "I saw two pretty butterflies today.#$b#They reminded me of us...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor2Anahi": "It's good to leave the computer and breathe some air for a while.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor3Anahi": "Next time you buy a cow, can I name it?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor4Anahi": "Boo! Your farm is like a palace, and you're the garden's nymph...$4#$b#Jeez... That was cheesy, wasn't it?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SRAnahi": "Hey boo! One sec, I'm writing things on my blog!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid0Anahi": "Our baby is so cuuuuuuuute! I want to pinch their cheeks!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid1Anahi": "Granny wants to see our little one one day!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid2Anahi": "*Sigh* I guess I need some tips for being a mother...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid3Anahi": "Can you believe?! Me... Being a mother?! This world is crazy!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid4Anahi": "Our little sweetpea is looking happy today!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids0Anahi": "Granny said our kids have a bright future ahead of them!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids1Anahi": "I can't choose which of them I love more... They're both my sweetpeas!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids2Anahi": "I'll treat them both equally... I don't want to follow my parent's steps...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids3Anahi": "Can you believe?! Me... Being a mother of two?! This world is crazy!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids4Anahi": "Can't give pizza for them to eat... It's not healthy...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good0Anahi": "... You're beautiful...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good1Anahi": "Heeeeeeeeeey! I would still love you if an evil witch turned you into a pumpkin!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good2Anahi": "Never thought anyone would care about my silly interests...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good3Anahi": "I love you so much, it sounds silly...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good4Anahi": "Never thought I would find true love one day...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good5Anahi": "You make me feel the prettiest girl in the whole world...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good6Anahi": "Just posted on my blog... Best couples of Pelican Town...#$b#Of course we're the first ones!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good7Anahi": "Maybe I should write relationship tips on my blog today!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good8Anahi": "Boo! You look beautiful today!$6#$b#Your beauty shines bright just like the morning sun...$4#$b#Heheheheheh... Did you like it? I've been feeling poetic these days...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good9Anahi": "Let's share a heart-shaped pizza together!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral0Anahi": "Mmmm... Need to write more things for my blog...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral1Anahi": "... Please don't grow pumpkins on your farm...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral2Anahi": "I should visit granny someday.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral3Anahi": "Hey! Feelin' good?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral4Anahi": "You've been a bit distant lately. If you need time for yourself, you can say!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral5Anahi": "Think I'll make some pizza tonight.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral6Anahi": "I would totally go for a chimarrão now!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral7Anahi": "Mmm... What should I write about next?...$2#$b#Boo! Didn't see you here!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral8Anahi": "Can we cook some pizza tonight?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral9Anahi": "Hey, mind if I grow a few abutilons on your farm?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad0Anahi": "I... I don't wanna talk...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad1Anahi": "Go away...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad2Anahi": "Do you hate me?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad3Anahi": "Sorry, I'm not in the mood for jokes...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad4Anahi": "Maybe they're right... Maybe I'm weird and annoying...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad5Anahi": "Tell me the truth... Do you find me annoying?$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad6Anahi": "I miss granny, atleast she loved me...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad7Anahi": "I thought we were perfect for eachother...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad8Anahi": "I miss my mama... If I could hug her one last time...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad9Anahi": "Maybe if I looked pretty just like my sister...$8",
    //Mayara
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IntroductionMayara": "Hello, kid! My name is Mayara, but you can also call me ''granny''!$1#$b#I run the local restaurant alongside my dear husband Raoni, so if you ever feel hungry, make sure to come here!$1#$b#We'll welcome you with open arms! Now, may Yoba bless your day!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_DumpsterDiveCommentMayara": "Do you need some food?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRainMayara": "@! Are you okay, dear?$2#$b#I've never seen something like this before... I wonder how our Mama from the storms must be feeling...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRainFinishedMayara": "Thank Yoba everything is alright...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRain2Mayara": "I'm still trying to understand the meaning of this rain...$4#$b#I think Mama is just feeling something we don't understand for now... Eparrei, Mama!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HitBySlingshotMayara": "Hey! No violence is tolerated here!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortEnteringMayara": "Hello, Mama from the seas!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortLeavingMayara": "Goodbye, Mama from the seas! I promise I'll be back soon!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortShoreMayara": "I should've brought a crystal rose to gift Mama...$4#$b#I've been feeling forgotten these days... Guess my death is coming!$1#$b#Awwww, no need to feel sad... This day will come for all of us!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortChairMayara": "Take a moment to relax, @!$1#$b#I know you deserve it, you work hard everyday!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortBarMayara": "So sad they don't serve chimarrão here...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortUmbrellaMayara": "Make sure to use sunscreen, kid!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortTowelMayara": "I have a story from when I met a mermaid, wanna hear it?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortWanderMayara": "When I die, make sure to throw my ashes on the sea, @...#$b#Awwww, no need to feel sad... This day will come for all of us!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortMayara": "Such a beautiful day today, isn't it?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AcceptBirthdayGiftNegativeMayara": "This is extremely rude! Don't you even dare to treat me or my family like this ever again!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AcceptBirthdayGiftPositiveMayara": "*Gasp* For me?! Thank you, kid! You just made this old lady's birthday better!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectBouquetMayara": "Sorry, kid, but this old lady right here is already married!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectMermaidPendantMayara": "Sorry, kid, but this old lady right here is already married!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectRoommateProposalMayara": "Oh kid... I'm sorry, but I'm comfortable with my house...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectMovieTicketMayara": "I'm sorry, kid, but I have business to attend to...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MarriedToAnahiMayara": "You better treat my dear granddaughter really well, okay?$1#$b#And no pumpkins!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_DatingAnahiMayara": "Anahi won't stop talking about you.#$b#Are you two, perhaps, in a relationship?#$b#You can tell granny, I won't judge you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PamHouseMayara": "Anahi told me about what you've done for Miss Pam and Miss Penny... You have a kind heart, sweetpea...#$b#May Yoba bless you in your journey, dear!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PamHouseAnonymousMayara": "May Yoba bless the one who helped Ms Pam and Ms Penny!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CropMaturedMayara1": "*Sniff Sniff* Mmmm... You smell like rosemaries... That's good!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CropMaturedMayara2": "I see you've been taking care of some good sweet gem berries...#$b#You can sell them for a good price if you turn these into perfumes!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CropMaturedMayara3": "Mmmmm... You smell like pumpkins... Better keep distance of Anahi, then!#$b#She hates pumpkins!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CropMaturedMayara4": "I saw your farm from afar... I see you're also fond of Abutilons!#$b#Anahi loves them!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CropMaturedMayara5": "@! Quick tip... You can turn Fairy Roses into beautiful bouquets if you have the bouquet maker!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LovedGiftMayara": "*Gasp*! Are you giving this to me, Sweetpea? Thank you! May Yoba bless your day, sweetheart!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LikedGiftMayara": "Are you giving this to me, Sweetpea? Thank you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_DislikedGiftMayara": "Did I do something to upset you, dear?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HatedGiftMayara": "Hey! Manners! This is not nice, @!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_NeutralGiftMayara": "Thank you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MayaraGTinteraction1": "*Gasp* How beautiful, @... Reminds me of my Mama of the seas... Odoyá!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring1Mayara": "Look, @, look! This little one bloomed on my grass today![18]$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMonMayara": "Hello, Sweetpea! Need something?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon2Mayara": "I'm so proud of my grandchildren!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon4Mayara": "You're always welcome on my house, Sweetpea!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon6Mayara": "Come in, Sweetpea! Let's chat for a bit!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon8Mayara": "I think I'll bake some cookies today.#$b#Come visit me later so we can eat some and chat a bit!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon10Mayara": "It's beautiful to think that everyone in these towns has their own dreams, their own lives.#$b#Crazy, isn't it?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTueMayara": "Have faith in Yoba, dear... Make sure to always thank Him for what he have done to us!$1#$b#But if you don't, that's fine too!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue2Mayara": "I have no idea on why Anahi hate pumpkins...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue4Mayara": "Hello, sweetpea! Beautiful day outside, isn't it?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue6Mayara": "Anahi hates when I call her ''Sweet Pumpkin''$1#$b#''It's Little Bell!'', she shouts.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue8Mayara": "Juju is such a bright girl, with a beautiful future ahead of her...$1#$b#She just needs to accept it...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue10Mayara": "Kaíque and Poliana didn't support Anahi's career as a journalist... But I do!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWedMayara": "What a beautiful day today...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed2Mayara": "I'm truly thankful for my Lady for everything she have done for me...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed4Mayara": "I'm truly thankful for my Lady for everything she have done for me...$1#$b#Even though she gets mad at me sometimes, I know it's for the greater good!$1#$b#She's a kind woman!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed6Mayara": "My Lady never gave up on me! Not even when I began to get older.$1#$b#I have a deep affection for her!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed8Mayara": "My Lady helped me understand myself as a woman.#$b#She showed me that femininity does not equal weakness, how women have always been strong on our society.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed10Mayara": "My Lady helped me understand myself as a woman.#$b#She showed me that femininity does not equal weakness, how women have always been strong on our society.#$b#I'm very grateful to her for that! Laroyê!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThuMayara": "Isn't Anahi such a bright kid?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu2Mayara": "Isn't Anahi such a bright kid?$1#$b#Mm? Oh I know she isn't a kid anymore, but she will always be my baby!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu4Mayara": "Take some time to study too, Sweetpea!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu6Mayara": "Take some time to study too, Sweetpea!#$b#It's important to for us, humans, to exercize our brains!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu8Mayara": "Take some time to study too, Sweetpea!#$b#It's important to for us, humans, to exercize our brains!$1#$b#I never stopped studying, not even after retiring!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu10Mayara": "Sweetpea, you seem tired...$2#$b#Come, sit a bit with granny, I'll read some books for you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFriMayara": "May Yoba bless you, dear!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri2Mayara": "May Yoba bless your day, Sweetpea!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri4Mayara": "Hello, dear... Need a hug?#$b#There, there... Granny will always be here for you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri6Mayara": "Hello, dear... Need a hug?#$b#There, there... Granny will always be here for you!$1#$b#May Yoba bless you, dear!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri8Mayara": "Lookin' good today, Sweetpea!$1#$b#Bet the ladies will all fall for you!#$b#Or the boys! Doesn't matter who you love, granny will never judge you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri10Mayara": "Lookin' good today, Sweetpea!$1#$b#Bet the ladies will all fall for you!#$b#Or the boys! Doesn't matter who you love, granny will never judge you!$1#$b#So, how are you doing this friday?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSatMayara": "I'm happy to see my sweet Anahi is studying!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat2Mayara": "I'm happy to see my sweet Anahi is studying!$1#$b#Studying is so important to us, Sweetpea...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat4Mayara": "The second best thing I've done in life was study!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat6Mayara": "The second best thing I've done in life was study!#$b#Studying opens doors and help you understand the world better, Sweetpea.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat8Mayara": "The second best thing I've done in life was study!#$b#Studying opens doors and help you understand the world better, Sweetpea.$1#$b#Also the feeling of graduating is something no one can explain!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat10Mayara": "The second best thing I've done in life was study!#$b#Studying opens doors and help you understand the world better, Sweetpea.$1#$b#Also the feeling of graduating is something no one can explain!$1#$b#Mm? The first best thing I've done in my life?#$b#Oh, Sweetpea, it was Kaíque, of course! Eheheheheheheh!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSunMayara": "Oh sweetpea... Granny's not feeling well today...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun2Mayara": "Oh sweetpea... Granny's not feeling well today...$2#$b#I'm worried about Raoni...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun4Mayara": "Do you think Raoni will get better?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun6Mayara": "My husband's health worries me...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun8Mayara": "My husband's health worries me...$2#$b#I know this moment will come for all of us, but I'm not ready for him to leave me yet...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun10Mayara": "My husband's health worries me...$2#$b#I know this moment will come for all of us, but I'm not ready for him to leave me yet...$2#$b#Breathe, Mayara, you all will meet again one day...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer1Mayara": "Hello, summer! Such a beautiful season...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMonMayara": "Flowers in this season are so pretty!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon2Mayara": "Cecilia and I have been friends since we were kids!#$b#I trust her so much!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon4Mayara": "Levi has a kind heart, but I think he needs to treat his little one better...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon6Mayara": "Our house may seem new, but it's actually 50 years old!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon8Mayara": "Our house may seem new, but it's actually 50 years old!$1#$b#Seems new because Levi keeps renovating it!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon10Mayara": "Our house may seem new, but it's actually 50 years old!$1#$b#Seems new because Levi keeps renovating it!$1#$b#He's a good man, I just don't agree with the methods he uses to educate Francisco...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTueMayara": "Ouch! My back hurts today...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue2Mayara": "Ouch! My back hurts today...$2#$b#One of the negative sides of getting older...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue4Mayara": "I feel my Lady's energy on my veins... She seems happy today!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue6Mayara": "I feel my Lady's energy on my veins... She seems happy today!$1#$b#I'll make her a padê later to thank her for everything she has done to me...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue8Mayara": "I feel my Lady's energy on my veins... She seems happy today!$1#$b#I'll make her a padê later to thank her for everything she has done to me...$1#$b#Maybe this will make her even happier!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue10Mayara": "You look beautiful today, Sweetpea!$1#$b#As bright as a summer spangle!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWedMayara": "It seems like our sellings have been rising these days!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed2Mayara": "It seems like our sellings have been rising these days!$1#$b#That's an incredible thing! I'll light a candle to my Mama today!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed4Mayara": "Julieta's devotion to her religion is beautiful!$1#$b#Ah... Reminds me of when I was young...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed6Mayara": "Mm? You want to know who is this Mama I keep talking about?#$b#She's the Mama of the seas! Mother of all fish... Iemanjá! She helped me so much in life!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed8Mayara": "@! I'm so happy you stopped to visit us!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed10Mayara": "@! I'm so happy you stopped to visit us!$1#$b#Let's chat for a bit! How was your day?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThuMayara": "Today is a perfect day to go to the beach!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu2Mayara": "Today is a perfect day to go to the beach!$1#$b#@! Care to accompany this old lady to the beach today?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu4Mayara": "Have you seen my Lady's dress?#$b#It's blue, dark as the mignight ocean... It's beautiful just like her!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu6Mayara": "The first spiritual guide I saw was my Lady.#$b#She appeared to me in a beautiful dark blue dress.#$b#Eheheheheh... The prettiest lady I've ever seen... after my momma, of course!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu8Mayara": "The first spiritual guide I saw was my Lady.#$b#She appeared to me in a beautiful dark blue dress.#$b#Eheheheheh... The prettiest lady I've ever seen... after my momma, of course!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu10Mayara": "The first spiritual guide I saw was my Lady.#$b#She appeared to me in a beautiful dark blue dress.#$b#Eheheheheh... The prettiest lady I've ever seen... after my momma, of course!$1#$b#I remember I was crying... I was scared I didn't have money to pay for my college...$2#$b#Her presence immediately calmed down my nerves!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFriMayara": "You seem sad today...$2#$b#Cheer up, Sweetpea! It's friday!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri2Mayara": "You seem sad today...$2#$b#Cheer up, Sweetpea! It's friday!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri4Mayara": "Remember to drink water, dear!#$b#I don't want you fainting from dehydration in front of me!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri6Mayara": "Books are the humanity's greatest weapons.#$b#They give you the knowledge to solve any debates by arguments or by throwing them, eheheheheh...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri8Mayara": "Sweetpea... You seem depressed today... What's the matter?$2#$b#Care for a hug?$1#$b#There, there... Tell granny everything!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri10Mayara": "Sweetpea... You seem depressed today... What's the matter?$2#$b#Care for a hug?$1#$b#There, there... Tell granny everything!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSatMayara": "It's been a while since I last talked to Evelyn... I wonder if she's still okay.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat2Mayara": "Hello, @! Hope your day is going well, with the blessings of Yoba!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat4Mayara": "Hello, @! Hope your day is going well, with the blessings of Yoba!$1#$b#Make sure to rest when needed!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat6Mayara": "Rest today, will ya'?#$b#Don't want my sweetpea fainting from exhaustion.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat8Mayara": "Guess I'll go visit Evelyn when we both have the chance...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat10Mayara": "Guess I'll go visit Evelyn when we both have the chance...#$b#We have so much to talk about!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSunMayara": "The weather seems nice today!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun2Mayara": "@! Come visit me on my seeds shop! I believe we have plenty of things that might catch your attention!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun4Mayara": "@! Come visit me on my seeds shop! I believe we have plenty of things that might catch your attention!$1#$b#These are all from Pindó-Rama!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun6Mayara": "I love rosemaries! When Raoni asked me to go on a date with him, he gave me a Rosemary bouquet!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun8Mayara": "I love rosemaries! When Raoni asked me to go on a date with him, he gave me a Rosemary bouquet!$1#$b#He have always been so romantic...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun10Mayara": "You want me to teach you how to light a candle to your spiritual guides? Of course, Sweetpea! I'm glad you care!$1#$b#First of all, pick up a nice and clean place to light it. Don't do it on the floor!#$b#After that, it's simple: While lighting it, you must keep your thoughts focused on your wish, on positive energies, on who you're lightning the candle for.$1#$b#Also make sure the candle burns until its end!$1#$b#But be careful, some candles might be dangerous to light to certain guides at home...#$b#Not because they're bad, but because many handle with heavy energies, and might bring such to your home by accident.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer16Mayara": "Today is a day of silence... The King is on earth!$1#$b#This is my religion, of course! You have the freedom to believe in whatever you want, @!$1#$b#Atotô!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall1Mayara": "Ah, fall! Season of fallen leaves and pumpkins... And Anahi's birthday!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMonMayara": "My mind have been a bit confused lately... I called Anahi by her sister's name, Alamanda...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon2Mayara": "Sweetpea, do you like books? They're really important for us!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon4Mayara": "There's nothing better than reading a good book with a warm cup of coffee!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon6Mayara": "It's a bit cold today... Perfect weather for a book and a nice cup of warm coffee!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon8Mayara": "Come in, sweetpea! Let me prepare some coffee for you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon10Mayara": "Come in, sweetpea! Let me prepare some coffee for you!$1#$b#How are you feeling today? Want granny to read a book for you?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTueMayara": "Sweetpea, don't you miss your mama?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue2Mayara": "Sweetpea, don't you miss your mama?$4#$b#I sure miss mine$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue4Mayara": "Sweetpea... Isn't it hard for you to live too far away from your mama?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue6Mayara": "Sweetpea... Isn't it hard for you to live too far away from your mama?$2#$b#If I were you, I would bring her with me!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue8Mayara": "Oh sweetpea... Promise me one thing...$4#$b#You'll, forever, treat your mama good...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue10Mayara": "Oh sweetpea... Promise me one thing...$4#$b#You'll, forever, treat your mama good...#$b#Believe me, sweetpea, it's so hard to lose someone so important such a mother...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWedMayara": "Wanna buy some seeds?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed2Mayara": "Wanna buy some seeds?#$b#We have cassava for sale this season!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed4Mayara": "Spirituality is beautiful, isn't it?$1#$b#I've achieved so many things in life because of it!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed6Mayara": "Remember to treat the elderly with respect, sweetpea!#$b#One day, you'll have grey hair, wrinkles and back pain too! Eheheheheheh...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed8Mayara": "You're a kind soul, @. Thank you, again, for what you did for us!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed10Mayara": "You're a kind soul, @. Thank you, again, for what you did for us!$1#$b#May Yoba bless your life and your journey!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThuMayara": "Hey, remember to take a break when needed!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu2Mayara": "Hey, remember to take a break when needed!#$b#Oh, and don't forget to read books!#$b#And your coat.#$b#It's cold outside!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu4Mayara": "I think my Lady really likes you! Eheheheh!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu6Mayara": "I think my Lady really likes you! Eheheheh!$1#$b#Tell me, @, have you ever met one of your spiritual guides?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu8Mayara": "This weather is beautiful... I can hear the wind singing!$1#$b#I like to sing back!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu10Mayara": "My mind is a bit confused today...$4#$b#Maybe it's a sign death is knocking on my door...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFriMayara": "What a beautiful day today, isn't it, sweetpea?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri2Mayara": "Aren't Duda and Ravi such bright kids?#$b#Can't wait to see them graduating!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri4Mayara": "Aren't Duda and Ravi such bright kids?#$b#Can't wait to see them graduating!$1#$b#Bet I'll be so emotional, I'll cry!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri6Mayara": "Aren't Duda and Ravi such bright kids?#$b#Can't wait to see them graduating!$1#$b#Bet I'll be so emotional, I'll cry!$1#$b#Or maybe I'll be dead! Who knows what waits for us tomorrow...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri8Mayara": "@! Sweetpea! Beautiful day today, isn't it?$1#$b#Care to accompany me for a bit?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri10Mayara": "@! Sweetpea! Beautiful day today, isn't it?$1#$b#Care to accompany me for a bit?$1#$b#We can go to the library and granny can read some books for you!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSatMayara": "Do you read books, sweetpea?#$b#My words fail to describe how much they're important for us...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat2Mayara": "Do you read books, sweetpea?#$b#My words fail to describe how much they're important for us...#$b#Hey, you can read my books if you're interested.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat4Mayara": "I remember people saying I would be nobody in life due to my psychological matter...$4#$b#I proved them wrong!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat6Mayara": "I was born with a psychological matter that affected the way I learned things.$4#$b#But that doesn't mean I wasn't able to learn!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat8Mayara": "I was born with a psychological matter that affected the way I learned things.$4#$b#But that doesn't mean I wasn't able to learn!$1#$b#In fact, I have three graduations!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat10Mayara": "I was born with a psychological matter that affected the way I learned things.$4#$b#But that doesn't mean I wasn't able to learn!$1#$b#In fact, I have three graduations!$1#$b#I graduated in administration, humans rights and culinary!#$b#Took my time, but it was worthy!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSunMayara": "May Yoba bless your day, sweetpea!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun2Mayara": "Fall is such a beautiful, yet macabre, season, don't you agree?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun4Mayara": "Fall is such a beautiful, yet macabre, season, don't you agree?#$b#Everything is dying, rotting...#$b#Mmmm... Maybe when I die, it will be in fall?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun6Mayara": "Bebel overworks herself too much...$4#$b#I tell her to rest a little, to drink some water, but she never listens...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun8Mayara": "Anahi helped me buy a doll online yesterday.#$b#Mm? Why? Oh! I've always wanted that doll when I was a kid, but I never had the chance to buy it.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun10Mayara": "Anahi helped me buy a doll online yesterday.#$b#Mm? Why? Oh! I've always wanted that doll when I was a kid, but I never had the chance to buy it.$1#$b#It's a method of healing your inner child!$1#$b#Tell me, Sweetpea, have you been through the same situation?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter1Mayara": "I'm still not used to snow...$4#$b#Feels like my bones freeze with the world.$2#$b#Everything hurts...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMonMayara": "Do you like Anahi's coat? I knitted it myself!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon2Mayara": "Do you like Anahi's coat? I knitted it myself!$1#$b#The zig-zag patters represents the movements of snakes.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon4Mayara": "I like to hide little meanings on my hand-made things.#$b#Prosperity symbols, protection charms, things like that!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon6Mayara": "I usually like to knit at night, midnight, when the only sound I can hear is silence.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon8Mayara": "I usually like to knit at night, midnight, when the only sound I can hear is silence.#$b#It helps me calm down my anxiety!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon10Mayara": "Sweetpea, let me teach you how to knit these days!$1#$b#Let's make a giant rainbow scarf together!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTueMayara": "It's so hard to have herb baths in this cold...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue2Mayara": "Have you ever tried herb baths?#$b#I recomend bathing with rosemaries, it helps us clean bad energies!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue4Mayara": "I think I'll have a red rose bath today.#$b#This will help me connect more with My Lady!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue6Mayara": "Sweetpea, if you ever feel anxious, try a lavender or chamomile bath!#$b#It helps us calm down and cleanse bad energies!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue8Mayara": "Sweetpea, if you ever feel bad about yourself, come to granny!$1#$b#We can talk about your feeling and I can prepare a nice self-love bath for you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue10Mayara": "One day I'll teach you how to prepare a herb bath!$1#$b#Just like how my granny used to make for me.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWedMayara": "This weather goes perfect with a nice book and a warm cup of coffee!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed2Mayara": "@! This weather goes perfect with a nice book and a warm cup of coffee!$1#$b#Tell me, do you like coffee? Because I do!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed4Mayara": "Reading old books is like listening to an old person's story.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed6Mayara": "Reading old books is like listening to an old person's story.#$b#Tell me, sweetpea, would you mind hearing my stories?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed8Mayara": "I think a coffee tastes sweeter when shared with a friend.#$b#So, care for a sip?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed10Mayara": "Ah... I feel like I live for quiet days like this.$1#$b#Feels like Yoba covered our world with a pearly-white veil of serenity...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThuMayara": "Have you seen Princess? She looks adorable in that pink coat!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu2Mayara": "Have you seen Princess? She looks adorable in that pink coat!$1#$b#I'm glad Cida takes care of her so well!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu4Mayara": "Animals are just like us! They feel cold, sorrow, happiness... I'm glad this town knows that!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu6Mayara": "Sweetpea! I'm happy you came to visit me! Tell me all the news.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu8Mayara": "Sometimes I question why... Why animals live less than us...$2#$b#It's not fair... But I believe it all has a reason, Yoba does everything he does for a reason...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu10Mayara": "Sweetpea, if you ever feel lonely during winter, come visit me!$1#$b#I like sharing my crazy stories with my sweetpeas!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFriMayara": "I like to sing to flowers at winter.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri2Mayara": "I like to sing to flowers at winter.#$b#Maybe they stop and listen... And last a little longer!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri4Mayara": "Even in winter, a few flowers bloom.#$b#Weirdly poetic, isn't it?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri6Mayara": "This weather makes me think about life... What's yet to come, what we already saw and what we'll never have the chance to meet again...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri8Mayara": "This weather makes me think about life... What's yet to come, what we already saw and what we'll never have the chance to meet again...#$b#Like my parents...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri10Mayara": "Sweetpea... Life can be beautiful like a flower, but just like it, has its own fragilities.#$b#Stay safe, rest when needed, embrace the beauties of life.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSatMayara": "Sometimes I pay Emily to make a dress for My Lady.#$b#She always loved them! She also told me that Emily has a beautiful energy!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat2Mayara": "The smell of candles reminds me of my granny.#$b#Brings back good memories! She was the one that led me to this path.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat4Mayara": "Raoni asked who I was today.$4#$b#*Sigh*$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat6Mayara": "Oh? You think I'm poetic?$4#$b#Well, thank you, sweetpea!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat8Mayara": "Winter always gives me headaches...$4#$b#As if the cold is freezing up my memories.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat10Mayara": "Hey sweetpea, I'm glad you're here...$2#$b#Raoni isn't feeling so good... Can you chat with him for a bit?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSunMayara": "Don't forget your coat, sweetpea!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun2Mayara": "Sweetpea, aren't you cold?$2#$b#Let's drink a warm cup of coffee together!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun4Mayara": "Sweetpea, aren't you cold?$2#$b#Let's drink a warm cup of coffee together!$1#$b#Maybe tea if you like, the choice is yours!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun6Mayara": "Sometimes I sit and wonder... How many winters do I have left?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun8Mayara": "When I was a kid, my ol' granny always told me I shouldn't be afraid of getting older.#$b#Each one of my wrinkles tells a story!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun10Mayara": "When I was a kid, my ol' granny always told me I shouldn't be afraid of getting older.#$b#Each one of my wrinkles tells a story!$1#$b#Oh, how I miss her...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring12Mayara": "It's so good to reunite with the Pelican Town again!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring23Mayara": "Are you going to dance with your special one, Sweetpea?$1",
