    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer27Mayara": "This festival is a blessing from the Mama of the seas!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall15Mayara": "May Yoba bless everyone that's going to compete tomorrow$1#$b#For me, we're all winners.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall26Mayara": "The energies from this festival are... Kinda odd...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter7Mayara": "Don't forget to warm yourself for tomorrow's festival, Sweetpea!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter24Mayara": "Let's hope for no fights about politics this year...$2#$b#Such special moment have no space for negative energies!$1",
