    //Francisco
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IntroductionFrancisco": "Oh! You're the new farmer, right?#$b#Nice to meet you! My name is Francisco, but you can call me Fran.$1#$b#Just don't call me ''Chiquinho'' and we'll be alright.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_DumpsterDiveCommentFrancisco": "Ewwwwwwww!! You're disgusting!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRainFrancisco": "@! Are you alright?! Need shelter?!$3#$b#N-nervous?! M-me?! No! Of course not!$3#$b#Stop messing with me!$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRainFinishedFrancisco": "Maybe that rain was a sign from the universe for me to design a green outfit...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRain2Francisco": "This rain again... Let's hope it doesn't stain my clothes...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HitBySlingshotFrancisco": "OUCH! HOW RUDE!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortEnteringFrancisco": "Ugh... My sunscreen is too sticky...$2#$b#I'm not feeling well, the trip was exhausting...#$b#I'm sweating...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortLeavingFrancisco": "I wish I could stay more...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortShoreFrancisco": "S-stop looking at me like that!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortChairFrancisco": "It feels good to relax and sunbathe for a while!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortBarFrancisco": "I looked away for five seconds and someone destroyed my sand castle...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortUmbrellaFrancisco": "The sun is too strong...#$b#Ugh... And there's sand everywhere...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortTowelFrancisco": "This towel feels uncomfortable...#$b#My drink is hot...$2#$b#Ugh... There's sand on my toes...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortWanderFrancisco": "Maybe if I walk like this... And then roll my hips like this...#$b#WAAAH!! @! Didn't see you here!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortFrancisco": "Let's see if I can find some inspiration here...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AcceptBirthdayGiftNegativeFrancisco": "",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AcceptBirthdayGiftPositiveFrancisco": "!!!$3#$b#For my... birthday?$3#$b#Hmph...$4",
