    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMonFrancisco": "Winter is easier to stylize clothes.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon2Francisco": "Winter is easier to stylize clothes.$1#$b#Now, the weather... Ugh!$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon4Francisco": "At least I can wear more layers... It's one of the few good things.$1",
