    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue6Francisco": "Talking to you makes the winter a bit more bearable.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue8Francisco": "%Francisco gently wrapped his arms around you... Pulling you closer for a warm hug.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue10Francisco": "Hey, um... Would you mind hugging me for a few minutes?$4#$b#I'm feeling cold...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWedFrancisco": "Today feels quiet... Almost too quiet...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed2Francisco": "I didn't feel like leaving the house today...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed4Francisco": "It's strange... winter makes everything feel distant.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed6Francisco": "I found a really soft blanket, it's so fuzzy it tickles!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed8Francisco": "Quiet days with you are... Different.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed10Francisco": "Spending quiet days with you... Where we just enjoy eachother's company... I wouldn't mind that.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThuFrancisco": "@! Did you know Mayara sells Pindó-Raman winter seeds?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu2Francisco": "Mayara works so much... Specially in winter...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu4Francisco": "I admire how Mayara handles everything so well.$1#$b#Although a day off wouldn't hurt her...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu6Francisco": "I admire how Mayara handles everything so well.$1#$b#*Sigh* I should start being productive too...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu8Francisco": "*Sigh* I should start being productive too...$2#$b#If I had a supermodel-best-friend it would be so much easier...$2#$b#Hey, @! Wanna be my supermodel-best-friend? I can teach you how to catwalk!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu10Francisco": "Hey... Maybe we could go to Mayara's sometime... You know, for dinner...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFriFrancisco": "This cold is terrible for my skin... It feels dry and oily at the same time...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri2Francisco": "I can't tell if my skin is dry or oily anymore... Ugh! It's confusing!$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri4Francisco": "Mmm... Maybe I should try a new skincare product...#$b#Maybe... Moriche oil?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri6Francisco": "Hey, um... I think you look... Good today...$7#$b#No questions! Hmph...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri8Francisco": "Hello there, @! You look good today!$1#$b#Got a new hairstyle? Because I noticed you changed something.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri10Francisco": "Hey... Do you think I look pretty today?$4#$b#Because you look wonderful to me!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSatFrancisco": "I woke up late today... it's too cold to leave bed.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat2Francisco": "I tried to wake up earlier today... But my bed won, hehe...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat4Francisco": "Mmmm... Maybe I'll try to learn how to cook, so I can make some soup...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat6Francisco": "Mmmm... Maybe I'll try to learn how to cook, so I can make some soup for my parents...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat8Francisco": "Hey, once I learn how to cook, you can pass by my house so we have lunch together!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat10Francisco": "Maybe someday... I could cook something just for you...$4#$b#I just neet to learn how...$7",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSunFrancisco": "At least in winter we don't have mosquitoes.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun2Francisco": "At least in winter we don't have mosquitoes.$1#$b#Best part of winter!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun4Francisco": "Twisting ankles in winter hurts even more than in normal weather...$2#$b#I don't know the reason...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun6Francisco": "Maybe winter feels nice sometimes...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun8Francisco": "I guess I... Don't hate winter anymore like I used to...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun10Francisco": "... Your presence warms me up...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring12Francisco": "Mmmm... Maybe a bunny-inspired outfit for tomorrow?#$b#H-HEY! IT'S NOT WHAT YOU'RE THINKING!$3",
