    //Marriage dialogue
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDspringFrancisco": "Spring feels so refreshing... Maybe we should try flower-inspired outfits together.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDsummerFrancisco": "Hey, don't forget to drink water, babe!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDfallFrancisco": "Fall colors are so elegant... We should match something warm and cozy.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDwinterFrancisco": "I'll try to learn how to make tea so we can stay warm together.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PatioFrancisco": "One second, babe, I'm practicing my catwalk.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay0Francisco": "Maybe I can stylize a raincoat... What do you think, babe?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay1Francisco": "Have my raincoat! I bet you will look wonderful in it!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay2Francisco": "Not having to hear my dad yell at me for such futile matters it's... Nice and peaceful.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay3Francisco": "I was thinking about trying a new outfit today... What do you think about raincoats?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay4Francisco": "Good morning... Did you sleep well?$4#$b#You look even more beautiful today. We are the most fashionable couple in this town!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay5Francisco": "Take care out there, babe! You may slip on mud and mess up all your clothes.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay0Francisco": "What a beautiful sunny day!$1#$b#Beautiful just like you...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay1Francisco": "Mmmmm... Maybe I'll train my catwalk today.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay2Francisco": "Babe! What do you think about my outfit?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay3Francisco": "Stay with me today, will ya?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay4Francisco": "Hey, babe, lovely sunny day today, isn't it?$1#$b#Lovely just like you.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay5Francisco": "You look so pretty today...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight0Francisco": "Hey... Come closer...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight1Francisco": "Care to watch a horror movie with me? This weather is perfect for that!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight2Francisco": "Stay close... it's cozy like this.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight3Francisco": "It's a bit cold today, let's cuddle under the blankets...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight4Francisco": "The smell of rain makes everything feel softer, I don't know how to explain.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight5Francisco": "I like to listen to the raindrops falling on the ground.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight0Francisco": "Wanna watch the stars together?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight1Francisco": "Pssssst... Come closer...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight2Francisco": "Phew! I'm so tired!$2#$b#Hey... Would you mind taking a bath with me?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight3Francisco": "Sleeping after a day of hard work it's always an unusual feeling...#$b#Guess you feel like this everyday, since you are always working!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight4Francisco": "Just finished cleaning up the house, guess I'll take a bath and go to sleep.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight5Francisco": "Would you still love me if I was a mushroom?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FunLeaveFrancisco": "I'm in the mood to do some things today! See you later, babe!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FunReturnFrancisco": "Hey, I'm back! How was your day?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OutdoorFrancisco": "Fresh air feels nice... but I still prefer being close to you.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor0Francisco": "You smell like flowers...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor1Francisco": "Careful not to get your clothes dirty, dear!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor2Francisco": "Can you teach me how to use a sword? I want to accompany you in your adventures!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor3Francisco": "Maybe I should design some outdoor outfits...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor4Francisco": "You look like a nature nymph...$4#$b#I hope you don't mind me saying such sugary things...$4",
