    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid4Francisco": "I never thought one day I would be a dad... The universe is crazy!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids0Francisco": "We should take more pictures of our little ones together!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids1Francisco": "Just fed our little ones, dear. You can go do your duties now.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids2Francisco": "One day I'll teach our little ones how to catwalk!$1",
