    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids4Francisco": "My dads must be proud of us for having such a wonderful family!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good0Francisco": "Being with you like this... it feels like a dream.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good1Francisco": "Can I teach you how to catwalk?#$b#Awww c'mon, you get used to it!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good2Francisco": "You make me feel so special... As if I'm the only boy in the world...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good3Francisco": "You're the best thing that ever happened to me.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good4Francisco": "I feel more confident when you're around.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good5Francisco": "Your sense of fashion is amazing, babe! Everything looks good on you!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good6Francisco": "I was thinking about new outfits for us... Matching ones, of course.$1",
