    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortBarAdrianno": "Whoa! That's a good one! *Hic* One more, please!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortUmbrellaAdrianno": "Dear Yoba... It's so hot today...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortTowelAdrianno": "*Sigh* I forgot my sunscreen...$2#$b#Let's hope it won't hurt tomorrow...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortWanderAdrianno": "Maybe if I stay until midnight, he will...$2#$b#No, Adrianno, stop daydreaming...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortAdrianno": "Oh! Hey, @!$1#$b#Don't mind me, I'm just... A little shy... It's been a while since I last took off my shirt in public.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AcceptBirthdayGiftNegativeAdrianno": "Oh my Yoba... What have I done to upset you, my Lord?$8#$b#I work hard everyday to bring food to my family and now I have to deal with such a horrible situation on my own birthday... Why?$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AcceptBirthdayGiftPositiveAdrianno": "!!!$10#$b#@... You're so kind...$4#$b#Thank you so much for this wonderful gift... You really made my day better!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectBouquetAdrianno": "Not now... I'm not ready...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_BreakUpAdrianno": "I understand...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectBouquetAlreadyMarriedAdrianno": "W-well... There's someone...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectBouquetVeryLowHeartsAdrianno": "@?! Are you crazy?!$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectBouquetLowHeartsAdrianno": "I'm sorry, @...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FarmhouseClutterAdrianno": "@! Your house is gigantic!$10#$b#I'm a bit lost...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MonstersInHouseAdrianno": "@! Get behind me! I'll protect you!$10",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpouseStardropAdrianno": "My love, my heart, my everything... That's what you are for me...$6#$b#Oh! And... This is for you!$1",
