    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMonAdrianno": "Everything feels softer in spring...#$b#Even life...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon2Adrianno": "I wish I could walk early in the morning at the beach like I used to do years ago.#$b#But since I got that job... *Sigh*$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon4Adrianno": "I wish I could walk early in the morning at the beach like I used to do years ago.#$b#Visiting the beach in spring is always a magical moment.",
