    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon10Adrianno": "Spring feels sweeter when you're around, @.$6#$b#If... that makes sense... I hope so.$2#$b#Well, anyways, I love you...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTueAdrianno": "Need help?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue2Adrianno": "...$9#$b#Oh, hello! Sorry, I was lost in thought.#$b#Need help?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue4Adrianno": "Hello there, @, are you lost? Need help with something?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue6Adrianno": "Wonderful day today, isn't it, @? This weather feels nice today.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue8Adrianno": "@! You're here! Wonderful day today, isn't it?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue10Adrianno": "Look who's here! If it isn't the love of my life...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWedAdrianno": "Looking for someone? I can help! I know this town like the palm of my hand!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed2Adrianno": "Hello there, @! Looking for someone? I can help! I know this town like the palm of my hand!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed4Adrianno": "Do you need seeds? Mayara sells some!$1#$b#But only until afternoon.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed6Adrianno": "Mayara keeps telling me and Bebel to rest, she says we work so much.#$b#But she also knows no rest...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed8Adrianno": "Hello there, @! Looking good today!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed10Adrianno": "My... I always thought you looked beautiful, but I never had the chance to say it out loud...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThuAdrianno": "All I do is work, sometimes I wonder if it's worth it...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu2Adrianno": "Sleeping during the day just to work at night... is really hard for me to get used to...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu4Adrianno": "I wish I could see my family more, but that would probably cost our house...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu6Adrianno": "I'll try to take a day off... There are days I can't see my own mother and we live in the same house!$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu8Adrianno": "It's not fair for me to work like that... Actually, it's not fair for anyone to work in those conditions!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu10Adrianno": "Hey... I've been thinking about taking a few days off so we can go out on a date together...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFriAdrianno": "Mmm...$9#$b#Oh hey! Sorry, I was lost in thoughts...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri2Adrianno": "Mmm...$9#$b#The sound of the waves...$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri4Adrianno": "Mmm...$9#$b#The sound of the waves... They make me feel so calm...$7",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri6Adrianno": "Hello, @... I'm listening to the sound of the waves from afar... they make me feel so calm...$7",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri8Adrianno": "Hello, @... I'm listening to the sound of the waves from afar... they make me feel so calm...$7#$b#Mmm... Maybe I should go to the beach for a bit and... Just feel...$7",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri10Adrianno": "Hey... Will you accompany me to the beach? I know a quiet place just for us...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSatAdrianno": "Are you lost?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat2Adrianno": "Hello there, @, are you lost?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat4Adrianno": "Francisco punched me and ran away yesterday.$2#$b#I just said he looked cute...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat6Adrianno": "I wonder if Gabi is okay...$2#$b#Oh! Hey there, @... Didn't see you coming.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat8Adrianno": "Hey, have you ever seen Gabi? She's a magician that lives on the graveyard behind joja.#$b#Sounds creepy, but she's the sweetest person I've ever met!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat10Adrianno": "Did you commission a love potion with Gabi and secretly gave it to me?$4#$b#Because I've never fallen for someone this bad...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSunAdrianno": "*Sigh*... I need to change my thoughts...$2#$b#Think positive things, Adrianno, think about mom, and dad, and...$7#$b#*Sigh*...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun2Adrianno": "Oh, hello, @, sorry, I'm not feeling so well right now... I think it is better for you to leave me with my thoughts...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun4Adrianno": "Hello, @, I'm... not feeling well right now... do you mind staying for a bit and chatting with me?$2#$b#Tell me, how has your day been?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun6Adrianno": "Hello, @, I'm... not feeling well right now... do you mind staying for a bit and chatting with me?$2#$b#*Sigh*... things have been a bit complicated at home$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun8Adrianno": "Hey, @, I'm glad you're here! I was not feeling well...$1#$b#So... Wanna chat a bit?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun10Adrianno": "My love! You're here! I was starting to feel lonely... But now that you're here, I'm feeling better!$1#$b#Hey, let's chat a bit!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer1Adrianno": "Summer is lovely! I like to watch the fireflies at night on my shift.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMonAdrianno": "I drank a lot of water today...#$b#you should too!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon2Adrianno": "Hot days like this can be rough...$2#$b#take it easy, okay?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon4Adrianno": "@! Sit for a bit, you must be feeling exhausted.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon6Adrianno": "Hey @, staying hydrated?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon8Adrianno": "Hello there, @! Don't forget to drink water!$1#$b#It's important for our health!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon10Adrianno": "Come closer.$4#$b#%He gently pulls you into a warm hug, you can hear his heartbeats as you place your head on his chest.#$b#You feel so warm, my sweet prince. I wish I could stay in this hug forever...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTueAdrianno": "I wish I had more time for myself...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue2Adrianno": "So hot today... I wish I had some ice cream now.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue4Adrianno": "Hello there, @! This weather totally calls for an ice cream!$1",
