    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue8Adrianno": "@! You're here! Let's have some ice cream together!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue10Adrianno": "Do you mind me calling you corny names? Like, come here my little scoop of strawberry ice cream!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWedAdrianno": "What a long day...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed2Adrianno": "Great... Another long day of work...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed4Adrianno": "Work doesn't slow down... even in this heat",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed6Adrianno": "Did you take care of yourself today?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed8Adrianno": "Did you take care of yourself today?#$b#You don't need to push yourself too hard.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed10Adrianno": "Your eyes remind me of amber...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThuAdrianno": "Mmmmm... I'm so tired, I don't wanna go to work today...$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu2Adrianno": "Mmmmm... I'm so tired, I don't wanna go to work today...$9#$b#Oh, hey @! Need something?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu4Adrianno": "I like taking showers, it's the only time I have for myself.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu6Adrianno": "Hey, @. What is your favorite perfume?#$b#Just asking!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu8Adrianno": "Hey, @. What is your favorite perfume?#$b#I can buy it for you once I have the money!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu10Adrianno": "Mmmmm... i'm so tired, don't wanna go to work today...$9#$b#Oh, @! You are here! Didn't see you coming.#$b#Well... Now that you're here... Would you mind helping me relax a little?$6#$b#On how, you ask, I know a way...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFriAdrianno": "Have you ever stayed up late to watch the fireflies?#$b#They're beautiful!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri2Adrianno": "I love to watch the fireflies during my shift.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri4Adrianno": "I'm used to the dark, working at night helped me surpass my fears.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri6Adrianno": "I remember the first day of my shift like if it was yesterday...#$b#I was so scared of the dark that, when I heard a strange noise, I threw my lantern on it.#$b#Turns out it was just Julieta.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri8Adrianno": "@! Be careful out there! Some people claim to have seen werewolves around here...#$b#Eheheheheh... Just kidding...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri10Adrianno": "I would hunt millions of fireflies if that meant seeing you smile.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSatAdrianno": "Hello there, @! Going to the beach?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat2Adrianno": "Hello there, @! Going to the beach?$1#$b#Make sure to pass by our store, you may find interesting fishing items there!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat4Adrianno": "The sea breeze always cheers me up.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat6Adrianno": "The sea breeze always cheers me up.$1#$b#We could just sit and listen to the wind.$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat8Adrianno": "The sea breeze always cheers me up.$1#$b#This wind... It feels like the Mama from the seas... She is whispering something to me...$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat10Adrianno": "I wish I could spend more time with you...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSunAdrianno": "It feels calm today.#$b#I like days like this.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun2Adrianno": "The tattoo on my back tickles sometimes.#$b#I wonder if Gabi did it correctly, that's totally not normal.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun4Adrianno": "The midnight breeze helps me calm down my nerves.#$b#The smell of nature is totally different from the city.",
