    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun8Adrianno": "Hey, do you have any tattoos? Are you interested in making one?#$b#I have a friend who is a professional in it!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun10Adrianno": "Damn... I don't know what you are doing to me... You drive me crazy sometimes...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall1Adrianno": "Today is Gabi's birthday, I should buy her something.",
