    //Marriage dialogue
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDspringAdrianno": "No matter how many flowers bloom, you will be the prettiest of them all...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDsummerAdrianno": "Ugh... Went fishing last night... My wrist hurts...$8#$b#%You grab his hand, softly kissing his wrist.#$b#!!!$10#$b#Wow... My mouth hurts so much...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDfallAdrianno": "The wind feels colder lately...$2#$b#Come closer... I don't want you catching a cold.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDwinterAdrianno": "It's freezing...$2#$b#Stay with me... I'll keep you warm.$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PatioAdrianno": "This wind reminds me of the ocean...$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay0Adrianno": "Maybe we could just stay in today...$1#$b#Just the two of us.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay1Adrianno": "Careful outside... the ground must be slippery.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay2Adrianno": "Rainy days like this make me want to stay close to you.$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay3Adrianno": "Catch a big catfish for me, will ya?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay4Adrianno": "You must enjoy rainy days... Since the rain waters your crops for you.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay5Adrianno": "Come here for a bit...$4#$b#Let me hold you.$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay0Adrianno": "Good morning, my sweet flower.$1#$b#Did you sleep well?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay1Adrianno": "It's nice having a place to rest...$1#$b#And you... You make everything better...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay2Adrianno": "I made sure everything is in order today.$1#$b#You can relax a bit.$1#$b#I can help you relax...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay3Adrianno": "My sweet merman... Let's go to the beach sometime.$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay4Adrianno": "You were sleeping in a funny position today.$1#$b#You are adorable, did you know that?$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay5Adrianno": "Don't overwork yourself today, okay?$1#$b#I'll be here when you come back.$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight0Adrianno": "I'll stay awake a little longer... just in case a werewolf appears to attack you.$1#$b#Eheheheh... Just kidding!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight1Adrianno": "You're all soaked!$8#$b#Let me take good care of you...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight2Adrianno": "The rain is loud tonight...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight3Adrianno": "My sweet prince... You work so hard everyday... I'm so proud of you!$6#$b#But don't forget to rest too!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight4Adrianno": "This weather is perfect for...$1#$b#...$4#$b#*Chuckles* What?$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight5Adrianno": "Come closer...$6#$b#You'll feel safer.$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight0Adrianno": "Here, have some.[209]#$b#I cooked it just for you.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight1Adrianno": "It's quiet tonight...#$b#I like it.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight2Adrianno": "You're so beautiful...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight3Adrianno": "I think I'll clean up the house tomorrow.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight4Adrianno": "Long day?#$b#Come rest with me.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight5Adrianno": "You look tired...#$b#Come here, let me hold you for a bit.$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FunLeaveAdrianno": "I need to do some things today, dear. I'll be back at night.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FunReturnAdrianno": "I'm here!#$b#Now... Let me show you how much I've missed you...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OutdoorAdrianno": "Can you teach me a few things about farming? i want to help you...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor0Adrianno": "This breeze feels so nice... It helps me clear my mind...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor1Adrianno": "Don't overwork yourself, my dear.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor2Adrianno": "Sometimes I just stop and listen to the wind...#$b#It reminds me that... I'm still here.$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor3Adrianno": "Hello, my love. Did you sleep well?$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor4Adrianno": "Sometimes I feel like the ocean is watching over us...$6#$b#Keeping us safe.$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SRAdrianno": "Hello, dear. Just cleaning up some things here!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid0Adrianno": "Sometimes I just watch them sleep...#$b#It feels peaceful.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid1Adrianno": "They're so small...$1#$b#I feel like I need to protect them from everything.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid2Adrianno": "I hope our little one grows up happy and healthy.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid3Adrianno": "Did you see their smile today?$1#$b#It made my whole day better.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid4Adrianno": "Never knew I would be a father someday... Thank you, @...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids0Adrianno": "We should take them to the beach sometime.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids1Adrianno": "The house feels livelier now. I like it!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids2Adrianno": "Seeing them play together makes me feel at peace...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids3Adrianno": "I'll do my best to be a good father for them, and a good man for you...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids4Adrianno": "Our babies are growing up so fast!$1#$b#They are my little pride and joy!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good0Adrianno": "My family absolutely adores you!$3#$b#Mama used to joke about me and you getting married.$1#$b#Now... Look where we are...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good1Adrianno": "Hey... come here for a second.$4#$b#*Chuckles* What? I just wanted to be close to you.$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good2Adrianno": "I want to adore you, cherish you... And cover you in kisses...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good3Adrianno": "When I'm with you, no matter the place, I'll feel at home...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good4Adrianno": "You're so beautiful...$6#$b#Sometimes I still can't believe that you're mine.$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good5Adrianno": "You are unbelievably beautiful... As if Yoba himself sculpted your body with his celestial hands...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good6Adrianno": "No matter how hard things get...$2#$b#I'll always come back to you.$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good7Adrianno": "Let's rest a bit on the couch...$1#$b#You lay your head on my chest while I pet your hair...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good8Adrianno": "Let's make some brigadeiros, my love!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good9Adrianno": "Sometimes I just imagine when we get older...$1#$b#I imagine you with your little wrinkles, and me kissing all of them... While I brush your soft greyish hair...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral0Adrianno": "I think I'll go watch the sea today.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral1Adrianno": "I'm craving brigadeiro.#$b#Guess I'll make some.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral2Adrianno": "Aren't you tired of working?#$b#Rest a little.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral3Adrianno": "I wonder how Gabi is doing.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral4Adrianno": "Can I make dinner tonight?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral5Adrianno": "I need to clean up the house.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral6Adrianno": "Hey.#$b#How are you doing?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral7Adrianno": "I miss fishing with my dad.#$b#Those were good days.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral8Adrianno": "Maybe I'll go to the beach tomorrow.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral9Adrianno": "Maybe I'll visit my family one day.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad0Adrianno": "...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad1Adrianno": "...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad2Adrianno": "... Hey...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad3Adrianno": "I'm not feeling well today...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad4Adrianno": "Did I do something wrong...?$2",
