    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Hello there, best friend! Let's go to the beach and relax a little!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Look who's there! If it isn't my best friend of all!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Hey, best friend! Have you ever met my friend Gabi? I bet you two would be great friends!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Hello there, best friend! I've been thinking about taking a few days off so we can go out together!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Hello there, best friend! I've been thinking about going to the beach for a bit!$1#$b#Why? Well, sometimes we just need to feel... just feel...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Hey, @! Do you have a crush on someone?$1#$b#Awwwww c'mon, you can tell me!$1#$b#Is it Haley? Have you seen the way she looks at you?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Friend! You're here! I was starting to feel lonely, but now that you're here, I'm feeling better!$1#$b#Hey, let's chat a bit!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Hey... Do you know that guy with black hair that rides a motorcycle?#$b#Can you tell me his name?$1#$b#W-why? O-oh, it's nothing!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Hello there, best friend! Would you be so kind to bring me some ice cream?$1#$b#Eheheheheh... Just kidding! Let's go together!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Hey, best friend!$1#$b#Long day, huh?#$b#Come sit with me for a bit, you deserve to rest.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Hey, friend, if I fall asleep, don't tell anyone, okay? Eheheheh...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Best friend! You're here!$3#$b#Damn... You always show up in time! Are you some kind of superhero?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Best friend! You're here!$3#$b#Looking good today! Let me guess... New haircut?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Best friend!$3#$b#Days like this feel lighter when you're around.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Hey, best friend...$2#$b#This weather makes everything feel a bit heavier, doesn't it?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Best friend!$1#$b#If something ever scares you during these nights... you can come find me, okay?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Best friend!$1#$b#Let's tell horror stories together!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu10AdriannoFemFarmer": "%Adrianno patted your head, messing up all of your hair.#$b#Eheheheheh... What?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Haven't had a best friend since Haley, thank you for being so kind to me, best friend!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Best friend! You're here!$1#$b#The sea feels different this time of year... Have you noticed?#$b#A bit scary, but also calming.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun10AdriannoFemFarmer": "Hey, best friend.$1#$b#I'm glad I have someone like you to talk to.$1",
