    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AdriannoGTinteraction1": "This... This reminds me of him...$9#$b#Thank you, @!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AdriannoGTinteraction2": "Eheheheh, look at his lil' face! How funny!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AdriannoGTinteraction3": "What an interesting book, @, thank you! I promise I'll read it on my free time!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AdriannoGTinteraction1M": "This... This reminds me of you... Of us... Thank you, @...$4",
