    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon8Ju": "Hey, @...$2#$b#If I suddenly disappeared into the ocean, would you come after me?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon10Ju": "You're getting tanned, how cute!$4#$b#*Chuckles* What? Everything you do is cute, chill.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTueJu": "Hey! How are you doing? Catching too many fishes?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue2Ju": "Don't underestimate my skills of pranking someone and pretending nothing happened after.$3",
