    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWedJu": "I love fall... Everything is dying... Neat!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed2Ju": "Hey, be careful on the forest... Or the headless mule might catch you...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed4Ju": "I like this season, people tend to get closer and hug each other when they are scared.#$b#Which means there's more people to prank, Eheheheheh...$3",
