    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon2Ju": "Aye, @! Come here! Give me a hug!$1#$b#%Julieta put her freezing hands on your warm nape while hugging you. This damn girl...#$b#Eheheheheh... Freezing cold, aren't they?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon4Ju": "Everything feels slower in winter...$2#$b#Do you think the concept of time feels cold too? Maybe that's why it feels slower, they're too lazy to work!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon6Ju": "Hey, be careful in this cold.$10#$b#I don't want you to catch a flu.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon8Ju": "Aye, @! Come here! Give me a hug!$1#$b#*Gasp* Your hands are freezing!$9#$b#You should take care of yourself more often, @...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon10Ju": "Stay close to me, my sweet vampire...$4#$b#You're warmer than any fire.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTueJu": "So cold... I'm not used to this weather...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue2Ju": "So cold... I'm not used to this weather...$2#$b#Where I'm from, it doesn't even snow!$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue4Ju": "Hey... do you ever feel like winter makes everything... quieter?$2#$b#I don't know if I like that.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue6Ju": "I think a quiet day is not that bad after all...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue8Ju": "I think I'm learning to apreciate silence.#$b#That's good!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue10Ju": "I love it when we just stay silent and apreciate eachothers company...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWedJu": "At least there's no mosquitoes in this season.#$b#They are all suffering... Burning in the depths of hell...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed2Ju": "What if I buried one of Harvey's things into the snow?...Eheheheheh...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed4Ju": "Mmmmm... I feel like annoying Francisco today...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed6Ju": "Hey, um... I'm sorry...$2#$b#W-why? Uh... It's nothing, bye!$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed8Ju": "Sorry for being rude the first time we've met...#$b#I swear I'll try to be a better person from now on!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed10Ju": "Let's throw snowballs on Bebel together!$8#$b#Pranking her is fun!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThuJu": "Your breath turns into smoke, neat!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu2Ju": "I'll search for snowmans to destroy... Eheheheheheh...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu4Ju": "I tried to scare Sebastian earlier...$10#$b#He just ignored me and went home. How boring...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu6Ju": "When I was a kid, I asked my mom to knit little sweaters for the fish in the lake.$10#$b#She just laughed at me, but my point still stand till' this day.$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu8Ju": "When I was a kid, I asked my mom to knit little sweaters for the fish in the lake.$10#$b#Hey, we should do that together! It would be fun!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu10Ju": "Let's go to the beach and fish some squids together, dear!$8#$b#Who catches more squids, wins!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFriJu": "Mmmmm... Who should I annoy today?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri2Ju": "%Julieta threw a snowball at you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri4Ju": "Mmmmm... I'm feeling so lazy today...$2#$b#Don't feel like being annoying today...$10",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri6Ju": "So cold... I think even a ghost would freeze in this weather...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri8Ju": "Hey... thanks for staying around.$1#$b#Even when I'm annoying.$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri10Ju": "Hey... It's cold today, isn't it? Let's go to my house and lay under the blankets...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSatJu": "Hey, loser.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat2Ju": "... Want something?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat4Ju": "What? Why are you looking at me like that?$10",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat6Ju": "I don't know why you insist in talking to me... Can't you see I'm trying to push you away?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat8Ju": "You really don't give up on me, huh...$2#$b#...I think I like that.$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat10Ju": "You're cold, aren't you?$8#$b#C'mere, stay closer...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSunJu": "The ground is slippery... Perfect for a prank.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun2Ju": "Ugh... Anahi is so annoying... I don't care about those dumb stories she tells...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun4Ju": "It's not that I don't like Anahi, it's just...$10#$b#Ugh! She talks too much!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun6Ju": "I tried to build an emo snowman... It looked so cursed I destroyed it right after.$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun8Ju": "Hey, let's build emo snowmen together! I won't destroy yours, I promise!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun10Ju": "The ground is slippery... Careful not to fall.$10#$b#But if you fall... I'll catch you.$4#$b#...Or fall with you.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring12Ju": "I ain't participating on this damn festival... Abigail always wins!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring23Ju": "Thank Yoba only people from Pelican Town need to dance.$9#$b#I look ridiculous on that dress...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer10Ju": "I was thinking about putting something nasty into the soup, but I saw what happened to Sam when him and Sebastian added anchovies and well...$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer27Ju": "This festival is the best! Man... I wish I could catch one of that Jellyfishes!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall15Ju": "I hope uncle Willy wins this year!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall26Ju": "Let's gooooooo~!!! Best festival of all!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter7Ju": "I wish I could participate, but I lost my fishing rod...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter24Ju": "*Sigh* Yeah... Family and stuff...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring12Y2Ju": "I ain't participating on this damn festival... Abigail always wins!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring23Y2Ju": "Thank Yoba only people from Pelican Town need to dance.$9#$b#I look ridiculous on that dress...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer10Y2Ju": "I was thinking about putting something nasty into the soup, but I saw what happened to Sam when him and Sebastian added anchovies and well...$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer27Y2Ju": "This festival is the best! Man... I wish I could catch one of that Jellyfishes!$1",
