    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall26Y2Ju": "Let's gooooooo~!!! Best festival of all!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter7Y2Ju": "I wish I could participate, but I lost my fishing rod...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter24Y2Ju": "*Sigh* Yeah... Family and stuff...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_DatingJu": "Hey, um...$4#$b#You look pretty today...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RSVjuneJu": "Hmph... A pianist... Seriously, who cares?$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RSVprankJu": "Oh my Yoba! You smell like... Like... Uhhhh... I don't even know how to explain!$9",
    //Marriage dialogue
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDspringJu": "Spring is so bright...$2#$b#Ugh... too many flowers.$2#$b#Let's find something more interesting to do.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDsummerJu": "It's too hot to think...$2#$b#Perfect excuse to do something stupid together.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDfallJu": "Honey! It's spooky month! We should celebrate!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MDwinterJu": "Cold, quiet...#$b#Perfect excuse to stay close all day.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PatioJu": "Hello there, my sweet vampire...$4#$b#I'm studying for a bit, I'll get inside as soon as I finish here.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay0Ju": "Hey, be careful not to catch a cold.$10#$b#I don't know how to cook soup, so I have no idea on how I will take care of you...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay1Ju": "*Gasp* Don't look behind you.$9#$b#... Heheheheh... Just kidding.$3#$b#Or am I?$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay2Ju": "Hey... It's raining today... So, stay with me.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay3Ju": "Hey... you're still here.$4#$b#Heh... Good.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay4Ju": "Hey... come here for a second.$4#$b#%Julieta hugged you tightly.#$b#...Nothing. Just felt like it.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyDay5Ju": "Don't forget your raincoat!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay0Ju": "You stole my blanket last night.$10#$b#Oh, I couldn't wake you up, you're too cute when you're asleep...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay1Ju": "Good morning, sleepyhead! I tried to cook some breakfast today, but I think I burned it...[382]$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay2Ju": "Hey, my sweet vampire...$4#$b#Don't wander too far. You know I'm worried about you...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay3Ju": "So... what are the plans for today?$1#$b#Causing chaos together?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay4Ju": "Good morning! Sleep well?$1#$b#I'll try to clean the house today. It's a bit dusty.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorDay5Ju": "Your house is so pretty, my sweet vampire... I love your sense of decoration!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight0Ju": "The rain it's too loud tonight... I don't know if I'll be able to sleep...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight1Ju": "Good night, my sweet vampire...$4#$b#May you have the darkest of dreams!$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight2Ju": "Stay close tonight...$10#$b#I don't like this kind of silence.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight3Ju": "You're all soaked! Let's take a bath together...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight4Ju": "BOO!$9#$b#Heheheheh...$7#$b#Relax... you're safe with me.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RainyNight5Ju": "This weather is perfect for a horror movie!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight0Ju": "You smell like nature... It's refreshing.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight1Ju": "Hey... Come here...$1#$b#Wanna have some fun?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight2Ju": "People say marriage changes things...$10#$b#But you're still the same weirdo as ever... That's why I love you.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight3Ju": "Don't fall asleep just yet...$4#$b#Stay with me a little longer.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight4Ju": "Can I lay my head into your chest tonight? I like listening to your heartbeats...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IndoorNight5Ju": "Go to sleep, I'll stay awake a bit more.$4#$b#If a ghost appears, I will hunt it down to protect you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FunLeaveJu": "I'll go out for a by today, my sweet vampire. Don't miss me too much, huh?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FunReturnJu": "I'm baaaaack!~ How was your day?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OutdoorJu": "I've never been the type of girl to enjoy farm living, but I'm getting used to it.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor0Ju": "Weird to think that I got married... I thought that it would never happen...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor1Ju": "%Julieta hid your tools somewhere in the house.#$b#Heheheheh... Go find them...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor2Ju": "We should go out more often... There's plenty of people to mess with here in Pelican Town.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor3Ju": "Don't let anyone else get too close to you...$10#$b#I don't like sharing.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Outdoor4Ju": "I still don't get why you chose me...$2#$b#... But I'm glad you did...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SRJu": "Hey! Just reading for a bit! One sec.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid0Ju": "This little bat will grow up to be a child of the darkness just like me!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid1Ju": "Our little bat is so sweet, dear. They smiled at me when I was feeding them.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid2Ju": "Hey... look at our little bats...#$b#So small... so fragile...$1#$b#...We should protect them.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid3Ju": "I tried to scare our little bat earlier... They just laughed at me.$1#$b#... I've never been so proud.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_OneKid4Ju": "Do you think they'll grow up weird like us?$1#$b#I hope so.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids0Ju": "I tried to teach them how to scare people, but they teamed up against me instead! Those little bats...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids1Ju": "Two little bats...$1#$b#Heh... This house got a lot louder.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids2Ju": "Do you think they'll grow up weird like us?$1#$b#I hope so.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids3Ju": "They fight a lot, chaotic just like momma!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_TwoKids4Ju": "Our little bats are growing up too fast, dear... I feel like, if I blink one more time, they already will be going to school!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good0Ju": "Hey... C'mere here for a sec.$4#$b#... I just wanted to see you closer.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good1Ju": "Do you think I got better as a person? I'm not pranking people like I used to.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good2Ju": "Be careful out there, I get so worried about you when you go into those mines!$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good3Ju": "Hey... You look perfect today.$4#$b#Just like you looked perfect yesterday and will look perfect tomorrow...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good4Ju": "I might be an annoying girl, but I'm your annoying girl...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good5Ju": "Hey... Stay here a bit longer.$4#$b#I like it when it's just the two of us.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good6Ju": "We should go fishing sometime!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good7Ju": "Stay with me today... I'll do whatever you want...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good8Ju": "I was thinking about you earlier.$8#$b#Don't ask what.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Good9Ju": "I know I don't say it a lot... But I love you so much, it hurts.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral0Ju": "Any ideas on what should I do today?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral1Ju": "It's one of those days...#$b#Not good, not bad... Just... A day.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral2Ju": "I'll study a bit more today.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral3Ju": "Sup.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral4Ju": "Do you think I should visit mama someday?$2#$b#... Nah.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral5Ju": "I think i should visit Willy someday.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral6Ju": "Any plans for today?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral7Ju": "You ever just stare at nothing and think about everything?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral8Ju": "Mmm... Maybe I'll go fishing someday.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Neutral9Ju": "Mmm... I feel like doing nothing today.#$b#Wanna do nothing together?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad0Ju": "And here I thought you would never leave me...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad1Ju": "Hey...$10#$b#You're not going anywhere, right?$2#$b#You're not leaving me... Right?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad2Ju": "I feel like I'm the same and live just like my parents...$2", //Ref Elis Regina
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad3Ju": "You are acting... Different from when we started dating...$2#$b#Why?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad4Ju": "I'm not mad, I'm just...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad5Ju": "I knew you'd get tired of me eventually...$2#$b#... Everyone does.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad6Ju": "I'll never be good enough...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad7Ju": "I'm such a mess...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad8Ju": "You're going to leave me, just like everyone else...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Bad9Ju": "I think I'll lock myself into our room and play videogames all day...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EngagementJu1": "I can't believe I'm getting married... I swear I'll be a good wife for you, my sweet vampire...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EngagementJu2": "I swear, I'll tickle you everyday...$4",
    //Non marriage candidates in i18n
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IntroductionCamelia": "Ah... The new farmer has arrived in our humble town... Welcome, dear @. May our lovely and gentle citizens make you feel at home here.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_DumpsterDiveCommentCamelia": "Wha- Ew! What are you doing?!$5#$b#*Ahem* I mean, please, dear @, we do not tolerate dumpster diving in this town, for people's private proprerty should be treated with respect.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRainCamelia": "... What? Scared? Me? Of course not!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRainFinishedCamelia": "What an absolutely odd event... Tell me, @, have you felt anything different after being exposed to this phenomenon?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRain2Camelia": "Ah... The untypical rain has come back to our dear valley...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HitBySlingshotCamelia": "Argh! How rude!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortEnteringCamelia": "Ah! What a wonderful sunny day... A perfect moment for me, Camélia, to enjoy the beach!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortLeavingCamelia": "The day has finally come to an end, but the wonderful memories are forever.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortShoreCamelia": "How absolutely majestic this beach is, a true tropical paradise!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortChairCamelia": "Hmph... How uncomfortable...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortBarCamelia": "%It looks like Camélia drank too much alcohol...#$b#@! *Hic* I'm a disgrace to my family... Julieta hates me, and it's all my fault...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortUmbrellaCamelia": "Hmph... This resort is a tad... Rustic...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortTowelCamelia": "Hmph! This sunscreen is rather sticky... I hope no grain of sand gets stuck on my body.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortWanderCamelia": "%Camélia is talking to herself...#$b#Will she forgive me if I apologize?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortCamelia": "Maybe I, Camélia, will step into the water to calm down my already anxious nerves of being a shop owner.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AcceptBirthdayGiftNegativeCamelia": "HUH?! Oh you... I'm going to... I'm going to... UGH!!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AcceptBirthdayGiftPositiveCamelia": "Huh?!... For... me?!$3#$b#Oh! Um... Ahem- I mean, you are extremely kind, my dear friend! I shall make good use of this marvelous present given to me on the day of my birth!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectBouquetCamelia": "How absolutely rude! I, Camélia, am already married!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectMermaidPendantCamelia": "How absolutely rude! I, Camélia, am already married!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectRoommateProposalCamelia": "How kind of you, @, but I, Camélia, have responsibilities to attend to and am in need to live in my own house to fullfill my duties as a shop owner.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectMovieTicketCamelia": "I must apologize, @, but I have no interest to see the movie displayed this season.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring1Camelia": "Spring has arrived... How delightful! The air itself feels refined, with hints of floral perfumes drifting and dancing through the air.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMonCamelia": "A new week begins. One must approach it with grace and discipline.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon2Camelia": "You seem to be adjusting well to the valley.#$b#Such is admirable!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon4Camelia": "It is easier to endure crowds when one is not alone.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon6Camelia": "I find myself relaxing more than usual.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon8Camelia": "Do take care not to trample the flowers, dear @. They deserve respect.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon10Camelia": "Hello there, @! I hope you are having a lovely day!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTueCamelia": "Good Tuesday, my dear @, are you in need of any of my services today?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue2Camelia": "Excuse me, I need to fill a few documents before night.#$b#A proper routine is essential for a balanced life.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue4Camelia": "Even the smallest details deserve attention.#$b#Neglect often leads to... Undesirable outcomes.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue6Camelia": "I trust you have been taking proper care of yourself, my dear @.#$b#Exhaustion is terribly unbecoming.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue8Camelia": "I find myself looking forward to seeing you, my dear friend.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue10Camelia": "Good Tuesday, @! What are your plans for today?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWedCamelia": "Midweek already... time moves faster than one would prefer.#$b#I, Camélia, shall make good use of the rest of my free time.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed2Camelia": "A proper routine is essential, even during such a charming season.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed4Camelia": "A proper routine is essential, even during such a charming season.#$b#Though... I suppose not everything can be controlled so easily.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed6Camelia": "You have a way of disrupting my routine.#$b#Not entirely unpleasant, I must admit I like chatting with you.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed8Camelia": "@! I'm happy to know you are here! I find myself looking forward to our conversations.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed10Camelia": "@! I'm happy to know you are here! I find myself looking forward to our conversations.$1#$b#Tell me, how is your day doing?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThuCamelia": "Beautiful flowers bloom in spring, don't you think?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu2Camelia": "Flowers, much like people, require proper care to truly flourish.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu4Camelia": "Flowers, much like people, require proper care to truly flourish.#$b#Be careful, dear @. Not all blossoms are as delicate as they appear...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu6Camelia": "Beautiful flowers bloom in spring.#$b#One remembers the first time her love, dear Crisanto, has offered a delicate Princess Flower bouquet as a symbol of his devotion.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu8Camelia": "Crisanto seems to appreciate my job, feels like he supports me no matter the situation.$1#$b#This brings me joy.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu10Camelia": "How lovely to see you today, dear @! Shall we drink some coffee?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFriCamelia": "What a lovely Friday, don't you agree, @?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri2Camelia": "Both Harpy Town and Pelican Town look livelier on Fridays, don't you agree, @?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri4Camelia": "Crowds can be overwhelming, if one is not careful.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri6Camelia": "Crowds can be overwhelming, if one is not careful.$2#$b#I used to avoid such situations whenever possible.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri8Camelia": "Hello there, @! I just got new clothes in my store.$1#$b#Wanna take a look?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri10Camelia": "Hello there, @! I just got new clothes and furniture in my store.$1#$b#Wanna take a look? I think you will like them!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSatCamelia": "Ugh... Julieta can be a tad annoying sometimes...$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat2Camelia": "It is easier to face such things as crowds and social gatherings when one is not alone.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat4Camelia": "One should always take a moment to appreciate beauty, even in the smallest things.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat6Camelia": "One should always take a moment to appreciate beauty, even in the smallest things.$1#$b#I used to overlook such moments... perhaps I was mistaken.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat8Camelia": "I find myself feeling more at ease these days.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat10Camelia": "Beautiful day today, isn't it, @? Would you like me to bake a cake for us?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSunCamelia": "Sundays are meant for reflection.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun2Camelia": "Julieta woke up late.#$b#... Again.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun4Camelia": "There are matters I would rather not dwell upon... yet they persist.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun6Camelia": "There are matters I would rather not dwell upon... yet they persist.#$b#But speaking with you makes such thoughts feel distant.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun8Camelia": "I've been feeling less anxious lately... Perhaps our conversations have been generating results for my wellbeing.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun10Camelia": "My dear @! I'm happy to see you're doing well today!$1#$b#You're always welcome on my house, you know!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer1Camelia": "Summer has its charms, I suppose... Though I find them rather... overwhelming.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMonCamelia": "This heat is... most unfortunate.$2#$b#It does nothing for one's composure.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon2Camelia": "Even the finest attire becomes unbearable in this weather.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon4Camelia": "Ugh... This heat tests my patience more than one would like...$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon6Camelia": "Perhaps I have been too harsh on simpler ways of living.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon8Camelia": "Talking with someone makes this dreadful heat feel somewhat bearable.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon10Camelia": "I must admit... I feel far more at ease when I am with you, even in this heat!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTueCamelia": "@! An honour to see you! Come pass by my store sometime!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue2Camelia": "Do take care under the sun, @. It can be quite unforgiving.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue4Camelia": "You seem unbothered by the heat. I wonder how you manage that.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue6Camelia": "Don't forget your sunscreen, @, or you may get deep fried under the hot summer day.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue8Camelia": "I find myself less concerned with appearances lately. How unusual.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue10Camelia": "Would you care to rest for a moment with me, @? Come on, I'll prepare a cup of coffee for us.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWedCamelia": "What an exquisite attire you're wearing today, @! Is it from my store?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed2Camelia": "Ugh! This heat is unacceptable!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed4Camelia": "It is difficult to remain elegant when one feels like an ice cream on the oven.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed6Camelia": "Perhaps the warm summer breeze is not that bad after all...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed8Camelia": "Julieta drives me crazy sometimes... What have I done to deserve that?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed10Camelia": "Julieta drives me crazy sometimes... Perhaps I've been too harsh on her...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThuCamelia": "What a beautiful day today. Isn't it, @?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu2Camelia": "Summer insists on testing one's patience, does it not?$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu4Camelia": "Isn't Duda such a wonderful student?$1#$b#She's bright in everything she does!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu6Camelia": "The day feels unusually calm...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu8Camelia": "The day feels unusually calm... One could almost forget her worries.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu10Camelia": "Isn't Duda such a wonderful student?$1#$b#She's bright in everything she does!$1#$b#I hope I'm not being too harsh on her... I just want her to have a good future...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFriCamelia": "The sun shows no mercy today... Careful out there, dear @!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri2Camelia": "Have you seen Julieta somewhere?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri4Camelia": "Have you seen Julieta somewhere?#$b#Tch... That damn kid...$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri6Camelia": "Have you seen Julieta somewhere?#$b#I haven't seen her since last night...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri8Camelia": "I... Think I shouldn't be so rigid on my visions of elegance and grace...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri10Camelia": "@! Have you seen Juju somewhere? I'm looking for her.$1#$b#Why? I got her a present!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSatCamelia": "Saturdays knows no rest for this damsel right here... So, if you excuse me...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat2Camelia": "@! Come pass by my store when you have time!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat4Camelia": "I wish I could rest today...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat6Camelia": "@! Do you have a lover? Come buy them a wonderful gift on my store!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat8Camelia": "The heat make it difficult to maintain certain standarts.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat10Camelia": "I'm trying to spend more time not only with Juju, but with Cris and Duda... Work isn't the whole meaning of life, you know?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSunCamelia": "Sundays are, usually, reserved for rest... But this damsel right here have responsibilities to attend to!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun2Camelia": "Isn't Cris the most wonderful, romantic and loveliest gentleman of all?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun4Camelia": "I was singing Duda to sleep last night and Julieta came to me, asking me to sing her to sleep too! Can you believe it?!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun6Camelia": "Cris made sure to give me a bouquet of flowers of each country he travelled to... Isn't he so romantic?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun8Camelia": "I'm glad Cris accepts my dramatic side...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun10Camelia": "I found myself more at peace now that I have someone to talk to!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall1Camelia": "Fall carries a certain melancholy, doesn't it, @?#$b#But we shall embrace our feelings with all of our hearts.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMonCamelia": "*Sigh* A new week begins...$2#$b#@! I-I mean... One is already prepared for another wonderful week of hardwork!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon2Camelia": "Duda is the sweetest kid of all! My little pride and joy!$1#$b#*Sigh* Unlike Julieta...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon4Camelia": "*Sigh* A new week begins...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon6Camelia": "*Sigh* A new week begins...$2#$b#...#$b#What?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon8Camelia": "I found myself slowly letting go of the past recently...#$b#... Such is admirable!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon10Camelia": "I've been feeling calmer these days.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTueCamelia": "Come pass by my beautiful store when you have time, dear @! We have a wonderful variety of items everyday!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue2Camelia": "A few of the clothes I, Camélia, sell, are made by my own hands.#$b#They are knitted with so much love and care.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue4Camelia": "Maybe I can knit you a sweater one day, @!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue6Camelia": "Maybe I can knit you a sweater one day, @!#$b#Would you mind commissioning me?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue8Camelia": "Maybe I can knit you a sweater one day, @!#$b#Don't worry, it will be free!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue10Camelia": "I think I'll knit a sweater for Juju.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWedCamelia": "Autumn calls for a quieter kind of elegance.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed2Camelia": "Will you excuse me, dear @? I have business to attend to.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed4Camelia": "Sometimes I'm so anxious, even silence seems loud...$2#$b#If that even makes sense...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed6Camelia": "I feel like I'm not as composed as I used to be...$2#$b#Ugh! That needs to change!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed8Camelia": "I feel like I'm not as composed as I used to be...$2#$b#It's... Weird to say the least.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed10Camelia": "I feel like I'm not as composed as I used to be...#$b#And that's fine!$1#$b#Perhaps perfection is not as important as I once believed.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThuCamelia": "Ugh... It's already thursday...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu2Camelia": "In Fall, the leaves fall so gracefully.#$b#There's beauty even in decay.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu4Camelia": "Mmmm... I wonder how Jodi is doing...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu6Camelia": "Mmmm... I wonder how Jodi is doing...#$b#Maybe I'll visit her someday!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu8Camelia": "Jodi and Serena are two of my closest friends on the town.#$b#*Sigh* And I've been so busy lately I couldn't even see my own friends...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu10Camelia": "Isn't Juju such a bright girl?$1#$b#She will be my little baby forever!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFriCamelia": "Cris is always so romantic! Oh... What a gentleman...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri2Camelia": "Ugh... Valdemar smells like fish...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri4Camelia": "Ugh... Valdemar smells like fish...$2#$b#I know it's not his fault, he works with fish anyways.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri6Camelia": "I know I'm being too harsh on Juju... But I just want the best for her!$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri8Camelia": "You are a great friend, @...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri10Camelia": "Hello there, @! I've been happier lately... Isn't that a wonderful thing?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSatCamelia": "The air is way too quiet...#$b#...#$b#Julieta must be planning something!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat2Camelia": "Warmer fabrics are now more appropriate for the upcoming seasons.#$b#Such things you'll only find at my store!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat4Camelia": "Kids deserve kindness, not pressure.#$b#And I found out about this only now...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat6Camelia": "I took a small break earlier.#$b#It felt strange, but I'm feeling better!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat8Camelia": "I'm still learning how to balance work and... everything else.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat10Camelia": "You have changed my perspective of life, @. Thank you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSunCamelia": "Sundays are usually moments of reflection and meditation, but this damsel right here has no time to even breathe correctly.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun2Camelia": "I have prepared a new collection with earthy tones for the season!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun4Camelia": "It's oddly relaxing to organize the things from my store.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun6Camelia": "Cris insisted I take some time off today...$2#$b#I suppose he is right, but...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun8Camelia": "@! Want some tea? I can make you some!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun10Camelia": "Juju is getting better everyday, and I'm so proud of her!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter1Camelia": "Ah... Winter has arrived at last! How peaceful everything feels... Don't you agree, my dear @?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMonCamelia": "Another week begins... One shall take one step at a time.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon2Camelia": "The Harpy town feels different covered in snow...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon4Camelia": "The Harpy town feels different covered in snow...#$b#Mmmm... Perhaps one is still not used to such weather...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon6Camelia": "I feel like I've been enjoying slower days...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon8Camelia": "My mom was the one that taught me how to knit. I've been knitting since I was a kid.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon10Camelia": "My mom was the one that taught me how to knit.#$b#Sometimes we talk on the telephone, but it's not the same thing as seeing her in person...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTueCamelia": "Do you have any old clothes you don't wear anymore, @? You can come to my store and donate them to me!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue2Camelia": "I, Camélia, also sell clothes on the internet. Most of my customers are from different countries!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue4Camelia": "I'm trying not to overwork myself anymore...$2#$b#It's hard, but I'm trying.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue6Camelia": "I should walk barefeet to exchange energies with the soil, but in this cold...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue8Camelia": "Dudinha is my little pride and joy! She will, one day, become a successful doctor!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue10Camelia": "Juju has been giving me a lot of fashion advices! She knows a lot about trends and stuff!$1#$b#I also noticed my sales have increased a little!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWedCamelia": "I'm so tired, but there's not much I can do... Work is work...$2#$b#I shall keep walking, and singing and following the music...", //ref Geraldo vandré
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed2Camelia": "Wonderful day today, isn't it, @? How are you doing?$1#$b#Me? Oh I'm just walking and singing and following the music...", //Ref Geraldo vandré
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed4Camelia": "Won't lie... Sometimes I miss Pindórama... Oh Pindórama... My Pindoraman Pindórama... Place of samba and sun...$2", // Ref Ary Barroso
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed6Camelia": "The light of the sun in the snow hurts my eyes...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed8Camelia": "@! Maybe one day I can teach you how to knit!$1#$b#I'm sure it would help you, it's relaxing and you need time to calm down your mind!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed10Camelia": "I don't like it when Juju drinks so much beer... She often says harmful things to me and Cris...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThuCamelia": "My sweet Duda has been helping me in the store... Isn't she so adorable?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu2Camelia": "Warm clothing is essential this season.#$b#Thankfully, my store has plenty of them... Some old, some made with love and care!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu4Camelia": "Would you care for something warm to drink, @?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu6Camelia": "I made some tea earlier. It helped me clear my thoughts...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu8Camelia": "I've been feeling genuinely happy these days.$1#$b#Perhaps it's because I have someone to talk to!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu10Camelia": "Cris surprised me with a giant bouquet yesterday... Isn't he such a gentleman?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFriCamelia": "Hello, @! In need of my services? I believe there's new clothes on my store that you might like!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri2Camelia": "Do come visit my store, @! I have prepared winter pieces.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri4Camelia": "The shop has been calmer these days...#$b#I don't mind it, though!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri6Camelia": "Balancing work and life is not as impossible as I once thought.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri8Camelia": "Weird to think that, even in my 50s, I can still learn things...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri10Camelia": "I'm happy you're a part of my life, @, I consider you a great friend!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSatCamelia": "One is not used to such weather...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat2Camelia": "You, dear @, shall take a moment of peace and quiet, just watching the snowflakes slowly dance into the wind, such shall clear your thoughts.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat4Camelia": "Winter brings up a bittersweet feeling of nostalgia... Tell me, @, what beautiful memories you like to remember?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat6Camelia": "Winter brings up a bittersweet feeling of nostalgia... Tell me, @, what beautiful memories you like to remember?$1#$b#Mm? Me?$3#$b#One does not... One does not talk about her past...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat8Camelia": "Cris bought me a scarf... Isn't he such a sweetheart?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat10Camelia": "Having you around makes these quiet days feel a little less lonely.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSunCamelia": "One believes that you, dear @, should change your attire to warmer ones, or you might catch a terrible cold!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun2Camelia": "Elegance and posture... That's all that matters.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun4Camelia": "One feels a bittersweet feeling of nostalgia on sundays... And one doesn't know the reason behind said emotions.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun6Camelia": "Sundays are a bit nostalgic to me... I don't know why...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun8Camelia": "I never thought that, one day I would simply sit and watch the snowflakes slowly fall onto the ground...$2#$b#Such simple things, but what matters the most is the peace I finally get to feel...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun10Camelia": "Never in my life I thought I would hear silence again.#$b#Sorry, @, but it's a private matter...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring12Camelia": "One believes Abigail is a tad grown up for such festival...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring23Camelia": "Ah... One believes this lovely festival is perfect to strengthen the connections between our lovely Harpy Town and the incredible Pelican Town!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer10Camelia": "If you find Julieta putting something nasty on the soup, do tell me, okay?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer27Camelia": "What a lovely and poetic festival, it is!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall15Camelia": "Hmph! Pierre... Pierre... Pierre... What a buffoon!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall26Camelia": "Tomorrow is Juju's favorite festival.#$b#I still don't get a good feeling about it... I always feel like there's something watching me...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter7Camelia": "Hmph! What an inelegant festival! Go outside in that cold just to harm these poor fish?!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter24Camelia": "Ah, indeed a wonderful moment to reunite with our dear families!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring12Y2Camelia": "One believes Abigail is a tad grown up for such festival...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring23Y2Camelia": "Ah... One believes this lovely festival is perfect to strengthen the connections between our lovely Harpy Town and the incredible Pelican Town!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer10Y2Camelia": "If you find Julieta putting something nasty on the soup, do tell me, okay?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer27Y2Camelia": "What a lovely and poetic festival, it is!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall15Y2Camelia": "Hmph! Pierre... Pierre... Pierre... What a buffoon!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall26Y2Camelia": "Tomorrow is Juju's favorite festival.#$b#I still don't get a good feeling about it... I always feel like there's something watching me...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter7Y2Camelia": "Hmph! What an inelegant festival! Go outside in that cold just to harm these poor fish?!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter24Y2Camelia": "Ah, indeed a wonderful moment to reunite with our dear families!$1",
    //Levi
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IntroductionLevi": "Howdy! The name is Levi, I'm the local bricklayer and farmer, alongside my husband.$1#$b#We sell Pindó-Raman seeds to Mayara, so if you're interested in some different and exotic plants, go check out her store!#$b#Also, have you met our son, Francisco?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_DumpsterDiveCommentLevi": "... I'll just ignore that...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRainLevi": "No, I'm not nervous... I'm just smoking because I want to.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRainFinishedLevi": "Cida told me this rain might make us lose hair.#$b#*Sigh* This would be terrible for me...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_GreenRain2Levi": "Now Cida is saying this rain is perfect for our hair health...$4#$b#Hmph... Where did she even get that information?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HitBySlingshotLevi": "Hey! What's the meaning of this?!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortEnteringLevi": "Nat insisted that I should go to the beach... He said it's good for my mental health...$4#$b#Hmph... Mental health...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortLeavingLevi": "I just came to the beach today because my husband told me to... If it wasn't for him, I would be at home watching TV.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortShoreLevi": "@, you were the one that built the resort, right?#$b#It's lookin' good!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortChairLevi": "I wonder what Francisco is doing...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortBarLevi": "Howdy! Do you sell caipirinha here?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortUmbrellaLevi": "Maybe I'll bring a seashell to Francisco.#$b#He says he inspires himself on nature, I want to help him.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortTowelLevi": "I'm glad they let me smoke here.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortWanderLevi": "Howdy, @. How are you doing? Takin' a break?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ResortLevi": "Hmph... Mental health... What nonsense, I'm perfectly fine!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AcceptBirthdayGiftNegativeLevi": "HEY! That's innapropriate! It's even more rude to gift this to someone on their birthday!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_AcceptBirthdayGiftPositiveLevi": "Heh... You sure are kind, kid! Thank you.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectBouquetLevi": "Sorry, kid, but this ol' man right here already has a soulmate.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectMermaidPendantLevi": "Sorry, kid, but this ol' man right here already has a soulmate.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectRoommateProposalLevi": "Sorry, kid, but this ol' man right here would like to live in his own house.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_RejectMovieTicketLevi": "Sorry, kid, I have business to attend to.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LovedGiftLevi": "You're a nice person, @, thank you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LikedGiftLevi": "Heh, thanks!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_DislikedGiftLevi": "That's junk.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HatedGiftLevi": "What's the meaning of this? This trash is not worth even to smoke it!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_NeutralGiftLevi": "Thanks, kid.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring1Levi": "Francisco likes this season. He often describes me the outfits he plans inspired by flowers.$1#$b#Honestly, I don't understand a single word...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMonLevi": "Howdy farmer!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon2Levi": "You sure work a lot, huh?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon4Levi": "*Sigh* I wonder if Dr. Harvey has medicine to prevent hairloss...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon6Levi": "*Sigh* Life was a bit harsh on me in the hairloss matters...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon8Levi": "Have I ever told you how I met Nat?#$b#No? Mm... Maybe one day I'll tell you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringMon10Levi": "Have I ever told you how I met Nat?#$b#I was a bus driver, and he dreamed to be a musician. We've met always on the same bus, on the same hour, and he always greeted me with the same smile.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTueLevi": "Hiya, @! Want some cigarettes?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue2Levi": "Hiya, @! Want some cigarettes?$1#$b#I don't mind sharing.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue4Levi": "I'm a lot taller compared to Nat.#$b#Honestly, I prefer this way. It's easier to pick him up in my arms.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue6Levi": "Maybe one day I'll quit those cigarettes.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue8Levi": "Howdy! Wanna have lunch in our house? You're always welcome!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringTue10Levi": "I try my best to quit these cigarettes, but it's stronger than me...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWedLevi": "How are you doin', @?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed2Levi": "Howdy, @! How are you doin'?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed4Levi": "I think I was the only person in town that Cida has paid correctly.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed6Levi": "I think I was the only person in town that Cida has paid correctly.#$b#Be careful with her offers, @.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed8Levi": "Hiya, @! How are you doin'? Workin' a lot?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringWed10Levi": "Hiya, @! How are you doin'? Workin' a lot?$1#$b#Take a break, it's good for your health.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThuLevi": "Howdy, @!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu2Levi": "Mm? Why do I always wear a cap? Hairloss, kid.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu4Levi": "Howdy, @! Send a hug to Robin. It's been a while since I last saw her.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu6Levi": "I saw Sebastian days ago. He was smoking.#$b#*Sigh* Kids these days...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu8Levi": "Howdy, @! Have you seen Francisco somewhere?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringThu10Levi": "Aye! How are you doin', @?$1#$b#Come visit us when you have time! We can drink some coffee!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFriLevi": "*Sigh* I think I need some beer.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri2Levi": "*Sigh* I think I need some beer.$4#$b#It helps me relax, you know?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri4Levi": "Nat used to bake jar cakes to make some money.#$b#They were delicious.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri6Levi": "If one day I plan to have a barbecue dinner, I will invite you, @.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri8Levi": "Howdy, @! Let's go to Mayara's grab some beer!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringFri10Levi": "Hey, can you tell Francisco I'm proud of him?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSatLevi": "Howdy! Takin' good care of your plants, @?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat2Levi": "Howdy! Takin' good care of your plants, @?#$b#You can always ask Nat for some advice, he's smart.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat4Levi": "I tried helpin' Francisco with fashion once.#$b#He told me I had no vision.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat6Levi": "Nat keeps saying I should smile more... *Sigh*$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat8Levi": "Francisco called me ''cringe'' today... What's that?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSat10Levi": "*Sigh* I wonder if I will live long enough to see my son succeed in life...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSunLevi": "Howdy, @. Takin' a break today?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun2Levi": "Nat is makin' coffee today, can you smell it?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun4Levi": "Nat is makin' coffee today, can you smell it?$1#$b#He makes the sweetest coffee of all town.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun6Levi": "Sometimes I miss drivin' the bus. The same I met Nat.#$b#Wasn't the best job of all, but I've met a lot of strange folks on that road.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun8Levi": "*Sigh* I'm not as handsome as I used to be... I wonder how he's still with me...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SpringSun10Levi": "*Sigh* I'm not as handsome as I used to be... I wonder how he's still with me...$2#$b#Sometimes I feel like he deserves someone better...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer1Levi": "Howdy, @! Just to remind you that Mayara's sellin' summer seeds now!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMonLevi": "Hiya! Need somethin'?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon2Levi": "Aye. Want a cigarette?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon4Levi": "Francisco keeps usin' words I don't understand.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon6Levi": "Francisco keeps usin' words I don't understand.$2#$b#He says Nat is ''Iconic''... Is that a good thing?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon8Levi": "Howdy, @. You look busy.#$b#Don't forget to eat somethin'.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerMon10Levi": "Nat says I worry way too much about Francisco.$3#$b#He's right, but don't tell him I said this to you...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTueLevi": "How's life, @? Doin' alright?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue2Levi": "Nat keeps sayin' I should use some sunscreen... I don't need that.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue4Levi": "I think Mayara should run for mayor one day.$1#$b#What does Cecilia actually do for us?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue6Levi": "My back is complaining more than Francisco these days...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue8Levi": "Supermodel career... *Sigh*...$2#$b#It's not that I don't think he has potential, it's just... Why can't he pick something else? Like, medicine, biology...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerTue10Levi": "Howdy, @! I was readin' a book last night! Found a phrase that could be useful for ya!$1#$b#Everyone knows how to love in their own way, the way itself, it's not important. What's important is that they know how to love.$1", //Ref Machado de assis
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWedLevi": "... Who are you again?#$b#Oh yeah, @. I'm sorry, I'm gettin' old.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed2Levi": "Even if I'm meltin' under the sun, I'll never say ''no'' to my man's nice cup of warm coffee.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed4Levi": "I don't understand art the way Francisco does...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed6Levi": "I could hear Nat's laugh in the other room yesterday, as he was talkin' to Francisco.#$b#His voice is the sweetest melody a man could ever hear.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed8Levi": "I don't understand art the way Francisco does, but I'm tryin'...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerWed10Levi": "Howdy, @! Want some coffee?#$b#You know, a warm cup of coffee and five minutes to rest can save a man's day.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThuLevi": "Howdy! Need something?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu2Levi": "Camélia's sellin' good stuff at her store. There's plenty of clothes for a hot summer day like this.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu4Levi": "Mayara sells good stuff at her restaurant. Stop by if you're hungry.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu6Levi": "Francisco keeps sayin' I should seek a psychologist.$3#$b#Tch...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu8Levi": "I was handsome once.#$b#I still am, if you close your eyes. Eheheheh...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerThu10Levi": "I was handsome once. I remember some girls on the bus I used to drive, they always asked me out.#$b#But I only had eyes for Nat...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFriLevi": "Need a cold beer to calm down my nerves...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri2Levi": "If Nat asks, tell him I drank only one beer.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri4Levi": "I see ya work hard, @. Every day.#$b#Make sure to rest a little.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri6Levi": "Nat gets even more handsome every day... Me? I feel like I've been hit by a truck...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri8Levi": "Have you seen Nat somewhere? Tell him to drink water, will ya'?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerFri10Levi": "Heya! You're friends with my son, right?#$b#Don't ever let him doubt himself, okay?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSatLevi": "*Sigh* Too hot today...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat2Levi": "*Sigh* I think Nat is makin' Tacacá today... Can't stand even the smell...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat4Levi": "Francisco says summer is for hot and bold colors, highlightin' the accessories and sleeveless turtlenecks.#$b#*Sigh* What on Earth is this boy sayin'?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat6Levi": "Paçoca is the coolest little guy ever. He's a good boy.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat8Levi": "You know... I complain a lot.$3#$b#But truth is, I got more blessings than problems.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSat10Levi": "I worry about Nat... He shouldn't overwork himself.$2#$b#''Overwork''... Just learned this word from Francisco.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSunLevi": "A cold beer would be perfect in this weather.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun2Levi": "Guess I'll sit under a tree and smoke a little.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun4Levi": "Howdy, @! You should drink a lot of water in this weather.#$b#The crops aren't the only ones that need water ya' know?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun6Levi": "Sundays are made for coffee and doin' absolutely nothin'.$1#$b#Not me, though, I wish I could do nothin' today!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun8Levi": "Sometimes I sit quiet on Sundays and think how fast life went by.$2#$b#That's a bit... What's the word? Melcancholic?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SummerSun10Levi": "Sometimes I sit quiet on Sundays and think how fast life went by.$2#$b#Hold onto good people while ya can, @.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall1Levi": "I hate this season...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMonLevi": "*Sigh*... Leaves, leaves and more leaves... Everywhere...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon2Levi": "It's already startin' to get cold...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon4Levi": "Nat says Fall is romantic... I think it's cold.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon6Levi": "Francisco just called me ''diva''... What does that mean?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon8Levi": "I think I'll go to the beach and smoke a little. Just to relax.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallMon10Levi": "When the air gets colder, I appreciate home more.$1#$b#Funny how aging changes a man.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTueLevi": "Need somethin', kid? Aren't you cold?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue2Levi": "I feel like coffee tastes better in cooler seasons.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue4Levi": "I feel like my knees can tell when winter is comin'.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue6Levi": "Are you takin' care of yourself, @? Need new clothes? Camélia has plenty on her store.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue8Levi": "Nat tried to knit me a scarf one day, but he threw it away, sayin' it was ugly.$3#$b#Don't tell him, but I secretly picked it up from the trash and hid it in my closet.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallTue10Levi": "You know... You can call me uncle Levi if you want to.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWedLevi": "Aye. Have you seen Nat? Is he taking care of himself?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed2Levi": "Howdy, @! Francisco told me to say somethin' to you.#$b#It's... Oh, wait... I forgot...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed4Levi": "Sometimes I wonder if I'm as grumpy as George...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed6Levi": "*Sigh* I think I'm gettin' way too bald...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed8Levi": "Aye, @! You're always welcome on my house!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallWed10Levi": "Howdy, @! Wanna stay for a bit and share a cigarette?$1#$b#Tell me, how's your day going?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThuLevi": "Howdy! Harvestin' some fall crops? It's a great way to make money.#$b#Just keep the pumpkins away from Anahi!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu2Levi": "I can hear Paçoca barkin' from home.#$b#Maybe he's happy about somethin'.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu4Levi": "Maybe I'll pay Valdemar a visit someday.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu6Levi": "Francisco said I should have a... ''skincare routine''... What's that?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu8Levi": "Aye, @... Do you think I'm gettin' too bald?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallThu10Levi": "I think Nat will bake a carrot cake today. Wanna visit us later? We can chat a bit.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFriLevi": "Ugh... My joints hurt today...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri2Levi": "Paçoca keeps jumpin' in leaf piles.$1#$b#... The ones I just finished cleaning...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri4Levi": "Francisco says autumn colors suit me, such as a warmer color palette...#$b#Kid's got strange taste.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri6Levi": "Nat's feelin' good today...$1#$b#That's all that matters to me.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri8Levi": "The fact that I built the houses on this town makes me proud of myself.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallFri10Levi": "The fact that Francisco found his aspiration in life makes me feel so proud of him.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSatLevi": "So quiet today... Hmph...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat2Levi": "I'm worried about Serena... Cida still hasn't paid her.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat4Levi": "What does ''cringe'' means? Francisco told me I was that...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat6Levi": "So quiet today...#$b#Mmmm... Way too quiet...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat8Levi": "So quiet today...#$b#Mmmm... Way too quiet...$3#$b#Be careful out there, @... Julieta must be plannin' somethin'",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSat10Levi": "I said to Francisco that I don't understand him sometimes.#$b#He said it was fine, as long as I loved him the way he is.#$b#I do!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSunLevi": "Those damn crows piss me off sometimes...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun2Levi": "Have you seen Mayara's seed shop? She's sellin' good stuff there!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun4Levi": "Nat keeps askin' me to wear more layers of clothes.$3#$b#Tsk... One layer is enough.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun6Levi": "Nat's makin' coffee again.$1#$b#That man solves half of my problems without knowin'.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun8Levi": "I don't understand Francisco sometimes... He keeps walkin' around the house for no reason...$3#$b#When I ask him why, he says he's... ''catwalking''?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FallSun10Levi": "If life ever gets heavy, kid... Come by the house.#$b#I'll make room for ya.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter1Levi": "Mayara gets weirdly poetic this time of the year...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMonLevi": "*Sigh* I hate this season...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon2Levi": "Howdy, @. Aren't you cold?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon4Levi": "From where I came from, it doesn't even snow...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon6Levi": "Hiya, kid! Don't forget to put on a sweater.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon8Levi": "Nat's coffee tastes even sweeter in this freezin' weather.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterMon10Levi": "Funny... The older I get, the more I value warmth and comfort.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTueLevi": "Need somethin', kid? Make it quick.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue2Levi": "Have you seen Nat? Is he okay?$3#$b#Tell him to take care of himself, will ya?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue4Levi": "Aye, put some warm clothes on. I'm feelin' cold just to watch you from afar.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue6Levi": "I'm glad people in these towns care about the animals.$1#$b#Have you seen Princess with her lil' pink sweater?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue8Levi": "Francisco said he'll make an outfit inspired by the snow.#$b#How can he see art in such random things?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterTue10Levi": "Howdy, @! How are you doin', my friend?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWedLevi": "Howdy, @!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed2Levi": "I gave Nat my scarf today.$1#$b#Me? Cold? Nah.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed4Levi": "Pindó-Rama dwarf morning glory... Such a big name for such a small flower.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed6Levi": "Make sure to give Paçoca some pats. He's a good boy.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed8Levi": "Francisco told me my sweater is perfect for winter.#$b#Finally, he spoke a word I could understand.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterWed10Levi": "I might not have a lot of money, but lookin' at my family, I feel like the richest man in the world!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThuLevi": "Julieta threw a snowball at me...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu2Levi": "I feel like Paçoca hates the winter more than I do... How's that even possible?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu4Levi": "Nat stole my blanket last night...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu6Levi": "Bein' bald in this time of the year is always a challenge.#$b#You don't have so much hair to protect your head from the cold.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu8Levi": "I love to hear Nat singing when he's doin' somethin'.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterThu10Levi": "Howdy, @! I'm feelin' like you're a part of our family now!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFriLevi": "*Sigh* I miss summer...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri2Levi": "Camélia is so dedicated to her job.$1#$b#I'm glad I'm friends with her.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri4Levi": "Nat drinks more Tacacá in winter. Ugh...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri6Levi": "Mayara often commissions me to fix her house's pipes.#$b#They're a headache for her... It's a pretty old house after all.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri8Levi": "Tryin' to read some books. It's never to late to learn.$1#$b#At least that's what Mayara says.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterFri10Levi": "If you ever miss your family, kid, make sure to come to our house. Friends are family after all.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSatLevi": "Mayara's sayin' non sense again...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat2Levi": "Howdy! Don't come closer. I think I'm gettin' sick.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat4Levi": "Nat likes to stay more indoors in winter. Maybe that's why I feel like the house feels livelier this season.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat6Levi": "I feel like you're becoming a part of the town pretty quickly, @!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat8Levi": "Howdy, @! If you see Nat, tell him I love him.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSat10Levi": "I wish I could do nothin' today, @... Feelin' lazy.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSunLevi": "Coffee tastes stronger in winter for some reason.#$b#For me the sweeter, the better.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun2Levi": "Nat tried to brush my hair yesterday, but there's almost none.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun4Levi": "Nat said he dreamed about angels yesterday. I asked him ''So you had a dream about yourself?''.$1#$b#Heh... I might be old, but my tongue's still sharp as a knife.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun6Levi": "Tried to help Francisco with his outfits, he said the patterns I chose were unfashionable...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun8Levi": "Sundays mixed with snow makes me feel... What's the word? ''Depressed''?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_WinterSun10Levi": "Howdy, @! Can you tell Francisco he... What's the word again? ''slayed''?$2#$b#Tell him his outfit is pretty.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring12Levi": "Chocolate eggs are so expensive nowadays...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring23Levi": "I loved to dance with Nat. He used to ask me to stay on the girl's side.$1#$b#Now we can't do it anymore...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer10Levi": "Make sure to bring somethin' good to the luau, huh?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer27Levi": "Maybe one day I'll learn how to build that lil' boat just like robin.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall15Levi": "We tried to compete years ago, but Pierre still won. Tsk...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall26Levi": "Careful not to get lost in that maze... Or the headless mule might catch you.#$b#Just kiddin'.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter7Levi": "Think you can catch a pink river dolphin tomorrow?#$b#Bet only one of them can make you win.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter24Levi": "From where I'm from, we have the feast of the winter star at summer.#$b#It's better in my opinion.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring12Y2Levi": "Chocolate eggs are so expensive nowadays...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Spring23Y2Levi": "I loved to dance with Nat. He used to ask me to stay on the girl's side.$1#$b#Now we can't do it anymore...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer10Y2Levi": "Make sure to bring somethin' good to the luau, huh?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Summer27Y2Levi": "Maybe one day I'll learn how to build that lil' boat just like robin.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall15Y2Levi": "We tried to compete years ago, but Pierre still won. Tsk...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fall26Y2Levi": "Careful not to get lost in that maze... Or the headless mule might catch you.#$b#Heh, Just kiddin'.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Winter7Y2Levi": "Think you can catch a pink river dolphin tomorrow?#$b#Bet only one of them can make you win.$1",
