    //Festival dialogue
    //Cida
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFcida1": "Just came here for the food!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFcida2": "I'm counting on you to defeat Abigail.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFcida1": "I wish the Harpy town was here...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFcida2": "I never danced with anyone, it's a waste of time.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Luaucida1": "I ain't putting nothing on this soup.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Luaucida2": "This soup always end up tasteless, no matter how many times you try.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJcida1": "How boring...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJcida2": "Yeah, yeah, how interesting...#$b#Let's go home, Princess.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Faircida1": "Why am I not participating?... Well... Um...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Faircida2": "I'm so hungry... And I just ate twelve hamburgers...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEcida1": "This festival is ruled by the devil.$3#$b#Mm? Why am I here then? Free food.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEcida2": "@! Would you mind helping this kind old lady to scare Julieta?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFcida1": "So cold...$2#$b#Princess is trembling...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFcida2": "So boring...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWScida1": "Just came here for the food!#$b#The family, well...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWScida2": "*Sigh* Lana loved this festival...$2",
    //Princess
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFprincess1": "%Princess is jumping, happily, like a bunny.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFprincess2": "%Princess is planning to attack Julieta.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFprincess1": "%Princess is biting a piece of someone's dress.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFprincess2": "%Princess is staring at the horizon.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Luauprincess1": "%Princess is biting a bone, let's just hope Cida won't add it to the soup.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Luauprincess2": "Woof woof woof!#$b#Princess offered you her toy, guess she wants to play with you.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJprincess1": "%Princess is tired, she's almost sleeping.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fairprincess1": "%Princess is eating a burger.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEprincess1": "%Princess is barking at the hands.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEprincess2": "Nobody will ever believe you...$2#$b#...#$b#Woof!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFprincess1": "%Princess is, indeed, trembling because of the cold. Poor Princess.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSprincess1": "%Princess is staring at the presents. Let's hope she won't tear them apart.",
    //Bebel
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFBebel1": "Hey, @! Enjoying the festival?$1#$b#It's always nice to take a day off, I understand you!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFBebel2": "Mm? Me? Joining the egg hunt?#$b#Oh I'm sorry, @, but running in those heels...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFBebel1": "That wood bridge is a bit dangerous, don't you think?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFBebel2": "Hey, @! Are you going to dance with someone?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauBebel1": "*Sigh* I forgot to buy something to add to the soup...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauBebel2": "Let's just hope Julieta didn't put something ''funny'' on the soup...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJBebel1": "How fascinating...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJBebel2": "Just imagine... A mermaid with a jellyfish tail...#$b#A... Jellymaid?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairBebel1": "@! I hope you win!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairBebel2": "@! I'm counting on you to defeat Pierre! Eheheheheh...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEBebel1": "Juju seems happy today!#$b#For the first time, she's not being annoying.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEBebel2": "Mmmmm! These candies are delicious!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFBebel1": "Just bought some things from the woman on the igloo. She sells good stuff!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFBebel2": "So cold today...$2#$b#I'm not used to such weather...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSBebel1": "Mm? My family?#$b#For me, friends ARE family. That means you are part of my family!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSBebel2": "Just spent all my money on that gift, I hope the person likes it...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFBebel1S": "Psssst... Hey... I think I saw someone hiding an egg right behind that tree on the left...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFBebel2S": "I'll be cheering up for you from afar, babe!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFBebel1S": "Oooooh... I wonder if a certain someone will ask me to dance...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFBebel2S": "These flowers reminds me of when you first gave me a bouquet...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauBebel1S": "Are you putting your farm's goods on the soup, babe?$1#$b#No milk or cheese, please!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauBebel2S": "You look beautiful today, my love.$4#$b#Whoa... It's getting hot in here!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJBebel1S": "I'm still not used to walk in the sand with these heels...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJBebel2S": "Hey... Let's go somewhere more quiet...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairBebel1S": "Babe! You're here!$1#$b#Let's grab something to eat!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairBebel2S": "Are you putting your goods on display?#$b#I bet you're going to win!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEBebel1S": "Hey... Would you still love me if I was a zombie? Or a vampire?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEBebel2S": "Babe! Let's grab some candies!$1#$b#%Bebel held your hand tight.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFBebel1S": "So cold...$2#$b#I sure wish that a certain someone would keep me warm...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFBebel2S": "Let's throw snowballs on Juju together!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSBebel1S": "You are my family, my love, my everything, my babe!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSBebel2S": "My gift? Well... I can show you once we get home...$4",
    //Anahi
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFAnahi1": "@! How are you doing?#$b#Prepare yourself for the hunt! It's not easy to win against Abby!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFAnahi2": "Mmmmm...$3#$b#Oh hey, @! I was thinking about something!$1#$b#Like... what do they do with those eggs later?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFAnahi1": "That dress tickles me...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFAnahi2": "I wish I could add some abutilons to the bouquet decorations...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauAnahi1": "@! Did you add something into the soup?#$b#Well, bet it will taste delicious then!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauAnahi2": "No pumpkins, please, no pumpkins, no pumpkins...$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJAnahi1": "Waaaaaaaaaah! So cool!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJAnahi2": "What on earth is Bebel talking about?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairAnahi1": "Ugh... Pierre, Pierre, and more Pierre...$5#$b#I'm tired of him winning everytime...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairAnahi2": "Yo! These burgers are phenomenal!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEAnahi1": "Waaaaaaaaaaaaah! Best festival ever!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEAnahi2": "Ugh... Those pumpkin candies...$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFAnahi1": "@! Care for a quick interview?#$b#What are the best fishing rods you've ever used?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFAnahi2": "It's a bit hot today, isn't it?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSAnahi1": "I'm grateful to my grandma, and... And... My grandpa and...$3#$b#Hmmmm...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSAnahi2": "If someone gifts me something pumpkin-related, I swear to Yoba...$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFAnahi1S": "Honey-Bunny! You're here!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFAnahi2S": "Boo! I'm already planning on what to write on my blog for when you win!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFAnahi1S": "... Will you ask me to dance?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFAnahi2S": "I wonder why can't I wear a suit to dance.$2#$b#Do you think I would look pretty in a suit?$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauAnahi1S": "Hey boo! What are you putting on the soup?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauAnahi2S": "Remember, boo, no pumpkins!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJAnahi1S": "*Yaaaaawn* I'm almost sleeping...$2#$b#Hey... Do you mind if I sleep in your lap?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJAnahi2S": "Would you still love me if I was a jellyfish?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairAnahi1S": "Aw yeah, boo! I'm counting on you to absolutely DESTROY Pierre!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairAnahi2S": "Boo... Be careful not to get addicted to that green-orange roulette...$2#$b#I've seen people that sold their houses just to have money to gamble...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEAnahi1S": "Hey, hypothetic scenario, if one of those creatures escaped, would you protect me?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEAnahi2S": "Booooo~... I'm ghost Anahi~... I'm in love with you and I will haunt you forever~...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFAnahi1S": "... Can I hug you? I'm a bit cold...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFAnahi2S": "Boo! Mind if I interview you?$6#$b#What's the feeling of winning this festival?$3#$b#*Chuckles* What? I already know you're winning!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSAnahi1S": "I'm grateful to a certain someone in my life...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSAnahi2S": "I'm grateful that I'm living the best life ever!$6#$b#And with a special someone!$4",
    //
    //Mayara
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFmayara1": "Mornin', sweetpea! Are you going to participate on the hunt?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFmayara2": "So good to see the youth from both towns reunited together to have fun!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFmayara1": "Me? Dance? *Chuckles* Oh sweetpea... My joints would propably give up on me!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFmayara2": "These flowers are so beautiful! Spring is truly lovely!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Luaumayara1": "That food is delicious! Can't even imagine how the soup is going to taste like!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Luaumayara2": "I brought quindim to the festival and potatoes to the soup! What about you, sweetpea?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJmayara1": "%Mayara is talking to the seas...#$b#Odoyá, mamãe, odoyá, rainha dos mares!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJmayara2": "Summer is over, sweetpea... How are you feeling?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fairmayara1": "Everyone worked so hard this year... I believe everyone deserve to win!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Fairmayara2": "I can't eat too much burgers... High cholesterol...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEmayara1": "I think I'll do a herb bath once I get home...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEmayara2": "These creatures are so scary...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFmayara1": "*Brrrrr*... So cold...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFmayara2": "Can't wait to go home and get under the blankets!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSmayara1": "%Mayara is praying...#$b#Thank you, Yoba, for everything you've done for us!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSmayara2": "Such a beautiful festival... Don't you agree, sweetpea?$1",
    //Francisco
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFFrancisco1": "I love bunnies! They're so cute!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFFrancisco2": "I think we should let the kids win this year!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFFrancisco1": "Hmph...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFFrancisco2": "%He is whispering to himself...#$b#What if someone asks me to dance?$7",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauFrancisco1": "*Sigh*... Too hot today...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauFrancisco2": "So hot... I want to go home...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJFrancisco1": "I'll stay on the sand... What if someone pushes me into the water?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJFrancisco2": "What about... An outfit inspired on the moonlight jellies?!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairFrancisco1": "My dads can be a little bit too much overprotective sometimes...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairFrancisco2": "Hey, @! I hope you win!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEFrancisco1": "So dark here... Can't see anything...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEFrancisco2": "STOP IT, JULIETA!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFFrancisco1": "I feel like people are more fashionable in winter.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFFrancisco2": "*Sigh* Can't find anything here that inspires me...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSFrancisco1": "I hope I don't get anything unfashionable...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSFrancisco2": "Pam has a terrible taste in fashion...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFFrancisco1S": "Do you think I would look good in a bunny outfit?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFFrancisco2S": "What if... Once we get home...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFFrancisco1S": "Do you think I look good in that suit?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFFrancisco2S": "You smell so good...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauFrancisco1S": "Hey babe! What are you adding into the soup?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauFrancisco2S": "Just added a mushroom to the soup!#$b#Don't worry, silly, it's not poisonous!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJFrancisco1S": "Psssst... Let's go somewhere quiet...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJFrancisco2S": "So dark... What if a werewolf appears?!$3#$b#Would you protect me?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairFrancisco1S": "*Sigh* I'm out of ideas for outfits today...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairFrancisco2S": "Hey, honey! What are you putting on your display?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEFrancisco1S": "Ah, @! you're here! Thank Yoba!$3#$b#I think... I'm lost.$2#$b#Mmmm... But since we're both here...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEFrancisco2S": "JULIETA! STOP IT! I'M TELLING @!$5",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFFrancisco1S": "Hey... You can have my coat if you're cold...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFFrancisco2S": "Brrrr... I'm freezing...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSFrancisco1S": "I'm grateful for having such an amazing partner in my life!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSFrancisco2S": "Oh I do have a special gift for you!$1#$b#Just... Wait until we get home...$4",
    //Adrianno
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFAdrianno1": "Mmmm... I'm feeling a bit sleepy...$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFAdrianno2": "Francisco hit me just because I joked about him wearing bunny ears...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFAdrianno1": "I think these flower decorations would look great adorned with a few clams!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFAdrianno2": "*Sigh* Should I ask him to dance?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauAdrianno1": "I'm sure dad added fish to the soup.#$b#One he caught himself!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauAdrianno2": "The sea looks beautiful today, doesn't it, @?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJAdrianno1": "Mmmm... I'm sleepy...$7",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJAdrianno2": "*Sigh* I'll have to go to work in a few minutes...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairAdrianno1": "Even though it's festival day, I still have to go to work at night...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairAdrianno2": "@! Got anything interesting to put on your display?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEAdrianno1": "I'm a bit worried about Mayara...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEAdrianno2": "Hiya there, @! Wanna grab something to eat? Let's go together!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFAdrianno1": "So cold...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFAdrianno2": "Me? Join the festival? Nah, I don't stand a chance against Willy!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSAdrianno1": "I'm grateful to my family and my job!$1#$b#Even though my job isn't the best...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSAdrianno2": "*Sigh* Mama brought rice with raisins...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFAdrianno1S": "Oh my Yoba... You would look adorable wearing bunny ears...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFAdrianno2S": "What should I call you today? My bunny?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFAdrianno1S": "Hey babe, why don't you wear the festival's suit?$1#$b#... Or dress... I bet you would look beautiful on it...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFAdrianno2S": "I wish I could gather all these flowers from the festival and give them to you in a giant bouquet...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauAdrianno1S": "Whoa... You're hot...$6#$b#I-I mean... It's quite hot today, isn't it?$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauAdrianno2S": "I've heard goat cheese gives a nice touch to the soup!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJAdrianno1S": "*Sigh* So tired... Can't... Open my eyes...$7#$b#Zzzzzzzzzzzzz...$9",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJAdrianno2S": "... You're so beautiful under the moonlight...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairAdrianno1S": "@! @! @! I'll be cheering up for you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairAdrianno2S": "You should try these burgers, babe, they are delicious!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEAdrianno1S": "Hey... I know somewhere quiet...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEAdrianno2S": "Mmmm... What should I call you today? My sweet vampire?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFAdrianno1S": "Aren't you cold?#$b#C'mere...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFAdrianno2S": "Babe, catch a big fish for me, will ya'?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSAdrianno1S": "I'm grateful to you, my dear, for being such a light in my life...$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSAdrianno2S": "You should try this cake Jodi brought, babe. It's delicious!$1",
    //Julieta
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFJu1": "Mmmmm... What if I hide a cherry bomb inside an egg?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFJu2": "Sometimes I wonder why... Why bunnies? They don't even lay eggs!$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFJu1": "Hmph! Boring!$6",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFJu2": "The smell of flowers is annoying...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauJu1": "What if I add clay to the soup?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauJu2": "Everyone's lucky I'm busy eating! Or else I would add anchovies to the soup!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJJu1": "Throwing a moonlight jelly on someone? Nah... Even I have limits",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJJu2": "So interesting! So beautiful! So... Oh my Yoba! I don't have words to describe!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairJu1": "What if I scared these cows? Eheheheheh...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairJu2": "What if... I changed the canned meat to bug meat? Eheheheheheh...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEJu1": "Hey, @! What are you dressed as?#$b#A loser?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEJu2": "*Gasp* Francisco! A ghost behind you!$9#$b#Oooooh... Someone's scared...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFJu1": "Yall are lucky I wont join this festival! Yall wouldn't stand a chance with me!$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFJu2": "Go, uncle Willy, go!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSJu1": "How boring...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSJu2": "Mmmm... I'm grateful to Duda, she's cool.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFJu1S": "Today I'm calling you my sweet bunny!$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFJu2S": "Psssst... Let's make Abigail trip and fall...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFJu1S": "Why can't I wear a suit? I think I would look good on it!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFJu2S": "I don't care about that stupid dress, I still wanna dance with you!$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauJu1S": "Hey babe! What are you adding into the soup?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauJu2S": "Let's sabotage the soup together, babe!$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJJu1S": "I think I saw a couple of jellyfishes over there! Reminded me of us...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJJu2S": "I'm a bit sleepy, can I rest on your shoulder?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairJu1S": "Look at those cows! Aren't they cute?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairJu2S": "Have you tried the fishing stall, babe?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEJu1S": "Hey... What are you dressed as? The love of my life?$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SEJu2S": "Look, @, look! Francisco is scaaaaared~...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFJu1S": "Catch a biiiiiiig fish for me, my sweet vampire!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFJu2S": "Babe! We should knit little sweaters for the fish we catch!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSJu1S": "Mmmmm... I'm grateful to a certain someone... Oh, what's their name again?$4#$b#Eheheheh... Just kidding! I love you, my sweet vampire.$8",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSJu2S": "I'm grateful to have someone that finally don't get tired of me!$1",
    //Camelia
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFCamelia1": "What an interesting festival! Bunnies often represents fertility and prosperity!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFCamelia2": "Careful not to trip in an egg and fall, @!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFCamelia1": "One remember having the joints to dance with her loved one, Crisanto!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFCamelia2": "The smell of flowers is truly sweet and delicate...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauCamelia1": "What an adorable moment of pure joy!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauCamelia2": "Tell me, dear @, tell me... What are you putting into the soup?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJCamelia1": "Truly interesting and unintentionally poetic!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJCamelia2": "Mmmm... What does the moonlight jellies symbolize spiritually?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairCamelia1": "Pssst... Hey... Can you check on Julieta to see if she isn't doing anything stupid?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairCamelia2": "Oh my, what a delightful barbecue!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SECamelia1": "How... Bizarre...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SECamelia2": "Julieta entered that maze a few hour ago... I'm more worried about a possible victim of her pranks than with her...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFCamelia1": "Hey, can you keep an eye on Juju? I don't want her pushing someone into this cold water...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFCamelia2": "@... Aren't you cold? Put on a warmer sweater!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSCamelia1": "I'm grateful to this beautiful and happy family I have!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSCamelia2": "Honestly, one believe she's grateful for everything she has!$1",
    //Levi
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFLevi1": "Howdy! Did you bring any eggs?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_EFLevi2": "Lookin' good today, @! How you doin'?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFLevi1": "I'm not a big fan of flowers, but I love when Nat brings me bouquets.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FFLevi2": "I used to dance with my dear Nat. He looks lovely in that suit.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauLevi1": "I don't think putting cupuassu on the soup is a good idea...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_LuauLevi2": "I have no idea on what to add to the soup...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJLevi1": "*Sigh* Why am I here again?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MJLevi2": "I'm a bit tired...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairLevi1": "I don't like it when Francisco hangs out with that Sebastian guy...#$b#... He smokes...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FairLevi2": "Howdy, @! Can you keep an eye on Francisco for me? I don't want him near that Sebastian guy...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SELevi1": "Mayara gets scared too easily.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_SELevi2": "Mmmmm... I have a gut feeling that Francisco is lost on that maze...$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFLevi1": "Bet this festival will be easy for you, @!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_IFLevi2": "Hiya, @! So cold today, isn't it?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSLevi1": "Mmmmm... This food is delicious!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_FWSLevi2": "Howdy, @! You can sit with us if you're feelin' lonely.$1",
