    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_Map28": "THTGraveyard",
    //Maps strings
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString1": "Confused lady: H-hey? Is someone there? I- well, Joja promised to pay me for the damage they afflicted on my farm, but... Well I-",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString2": "Receptionist: I wish I could help that poor lady, but... Well, business...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString3": "Uninterested lady: Damn gurl slay...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString4": "Talkative lady: And then I said to her: ''Who on Yoba do you think you're talking to?''",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString5": "Red haired lady: Ugh I hate this job...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString6": "Confused mister: Sorry, Pedro, but I have no idea on why your PC is acting like this...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString7": "Tall mister: Gurl...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString8": "Lady with a bow: La la la la la~ It's my first job, I'm so happy~",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString9": "Tired mister: *Yawn* Huh?! Hey! You shouldn't be here!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString10": "Kind old lady: Hello kid, are you lost? Where are your parents?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString11": "This house is a mess! What on Yoba happened here?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString12": "A book about magic.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString13": "As I write this, on my ruffled dress and soft makeup, on my trembling right hand lies my pen, and on my left, a glass of sugary cherry wine, I shall be the last to succumb to this curse that was dropped upon us, me and my dear siblings, as I already feel my insides transforming into stone. To the soul that is reading this message, farmer, I predicted your irrival, even before you were even born. You are the only one that can break this curse, thus by offering gifts from the Harpy Town to the Junimos. We trust your abilities and will be waiting for you.                                                   ~Narciso",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString14": "^ Harpy Town^@ Backwoods^> Mountains",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString15": "It's a clay water filter. Nothing beats a cold glass of water!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString16": "It's a small pirate ship. A fine piece.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString17": "It's a tiny CRT television. Someone's scribbled a smiley face on the screen in marker.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString18": "Salt and pepper shakers. One's almost empty.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString19": "A plate of freshly baked cookies. They're still warm, try not to eat them all at once.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString20": "A pineapple-shaped cup. It smells like coconut and summer.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString21": "There's an Escondidinho in there.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString22": "There's a sticky note on the door that reads: 'DON'T STEAL MY SNACKS!!'",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString23": "A display case with all kinds of things inside. Wonder where they all came from.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString24": "It's a lamp with a green glass shade. Probably best not to touch it.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString25": "It's a painting with a ship. A fine piece.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString26": "It's a toilet. Looks clean.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString27": "It's a delightfully large, blue plush bear.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString28": "A tall, carpet-covered scratching post for cats to climb.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString29": "It's a soccer ball. Looks perfectly worn-in.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString30": "It's a bookshelf overflowing with sports magazines.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString31": "It's a dresser drawer. Better not peek inside.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString32": "A tall wooden bookshelf packed with old novels.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString33": "A computer setup with a hefty tower and large monitor.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString34": "It's a sink. Should wash my hands.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString35": "It's a television. There's cooking show demonstrating how to make a soup.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString36": "A statue of a Malandro, seems important to Bebel",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString37": "A statue of Nossa Senhora Aparecidinha, seems important to Bebel",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString38": "It's a grandfather clock. It seems to keep perfect time",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString39": "A pineapple-shaped cup. It smells like tropical fruits.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString40": "It's a clay water filter. It keeps the drinking water fresh and clean.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString41": "It's a trash can. Looks pretty empty to me.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString42": "A tall wooden bookshelf packed with sewing guides.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString43": "A tall green plant. Looks healthy and cared for.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString44": "It's a laptop left open. It shows a recipe for 'How not to burn water'.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString45": "There's lots of sewing material here.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString46": "It's a small teddy bear.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString47": "A painting of a desert. It makes you feel thirsty just looking at it.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString48": "Some say this doll is haunted. Bebel doesn't seem to mind, though.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString49": "A large bookshelf filled with many books.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString50": "A large glass display cabinet. A set of ceramic dishes are neatly stacked inside.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString51": "It's a makeup vanity. The mirrors are completely spotless.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString52": "A giant plush bear. It's taking up way more space than it probably should.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString53": "A beautiful wooden piano. The handwriting on the sheet music is unreadable.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString54": "A leafy tree. The green leaves shows that it's being watered well.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString55": "A large palm tree. Seems sturdy enough.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString56": "There's a TV mounted to the ceiling. Hopefully it doesn't fall on anyone.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString57": "Lots of big glass bottles. They look pretty dusty.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString58": "A plant with bright red berries. They look yummy, better not eat them.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString59": "A big fish is hung above the stove. Must be a trophy catch.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString60": "It's an empty fridge. There's nothing to eat in here.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString61": "It's a large pile of firewood.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString62": "A bunch of storage bins filled with random, colorful items.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString63": "A beautiful painting of a house by the beach.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString64": "A messy pile of clothes. Someone really hates doing laundry.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString65": "It's a painting of a relaxing sunset.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString66": "It's a small painting of Yoba. It feels peaceful.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString67": "It's summer paintings of Pelican Town. Looks very familiar.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString68": "A lot of garbage cans.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString69": "It's a wardrobe. Better not peek inside.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString70": "It's a small PC setup.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString71": "It's a massive flat-screen TV. Perfect for game nights and watching movies.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString72": "It's a big PC. The screen shows a world built entirely out of blocks.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString73": "> Beach",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString74": "It's a pretty Azalea tree!",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString75": "A mannequin in the window with yellow hair and a beautiful red dress. It looks ready for a festival.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString76": "It's a dog house. It's too dark to see if anyone is inside.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString77": "It's a small TV. It's playing the news.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString78": "A painting of a large heart. It looks cozy.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString79": "A painting of a strange green doll. It's a bit unsettling.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString80": "It's a toilet. I think there's a fish in it.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString81": "There's a sticky note on the door that reads: 'BUY MORE MILK'",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString82": "It's a potted cactus. It seems healthy.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString83": "A mannequin dressed like a business lady. It looks very professional.",
