    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString87": "A mannequin wearing a vibrant blue dress with yellow and black patterns. It looks very traditional.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString88": "A mannequin wearing a t-shirt with a face printed on it. It's a casual look.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString89": "A shirt lying messy on the floor. Looks like a customer left it behind.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString90": "A mannequin wearing a black robe and a white center. It has a very spooky look",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString91": "A pile of bright and colorful children's toys. Looks very fun.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString92": "A plush toy of an orange junimo. It's very soft and adorable.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString93": "A pirate ship figurine. It has a lot of small details.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString94": "A robot toy. I wonder if it still lights up.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString95": "A massive wooden dollhouse. It looks beautifully crafted.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString96": "A hat rack with a hat resting on the top. Someone likely forgot it.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString97": "A completely torn and worn out couch. The stuffing is starting to leak out.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString98": "It's a clay water filter. It's completely filled.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString99": "It's a clay water filter. It seems empty.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString100": "Its a stove. Looks clean and ready for cooking a meal.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString101": "It's an expensive black pot accented with golden rings.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString102": "A wooden grandfather clock. Seems to work fine.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString103": "A carpeted cat tower. It looks like a good spot for a nap.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString104": "A red banner woven with green leaves. It looks very cultural.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString105": "A television housed inside a grand wooden armoire. The shelves are packed with extra storage.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString106": "It's an empty wooden shelf. There's a cobweb in the corner",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString107": "A small potted cactus. It doesn't seem to be for sale.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString108": "A large blue teddy bear plush.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString109": "A tall bookshelf packed with many books.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString110": "A tall bookshelf with many fashion magazines.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString111": "It's a fashion book. There's a bookmark halfway through.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString112": "It's a large painting of a boat.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString113": "A standard clock mounted on the wall.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString114": "A clothing rack displaying nothing. Looks like they need to restock.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString115": "A clothing rack with pink and blue dresses. The fabrics look very soft.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString116": "A large Brazil flag on the wall. It brings a lot of color to the room.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString117": "A TV built into a wooden frame. It blends with the furniture.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString118": "It's a clay water filter. It's completely filled.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString119": "It's a microwave. There's a single Brigadeiro being melted inside for a topping.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString120": "It's a garbage bin. It contains the empty wrapper of a Guarana soda bottle.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString121": "A green junimo plush sitting on the floor. It looks soft.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString122": "A collection of sewing needles, buttons, and fabric scraps.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_MapString123": "It's a sewing machine with a large wooden wheel.",
