    //Conversation topics
    //harpy town debris
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedAlex": "Harpy Town, huh?#$b#Maybe they have a gym there.$1#$b#Or at least somewhere to train.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedElliott": "Harpy Town... what a fascinating name.$1#$b#It sounds like the setting of a novel.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedHarvey": "I hope Julieta won't hide my things...$2#$b#I'm her favorite target...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedSam": "Hey, do you think Adrianno would like to join our band?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedSebastian": "*Sigh* Great... More people to interact with...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedShane": "Harpy Town... Hmph, who cares?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedAbigail": "I wonder what kinds of dangers are hidden there!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedEmily": "I feel a strong energy coming from this new town.$3#$b#Tell me, @, do you feel it too?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedHaley": "Wonderful! Camélia sells great clothes!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedLeah": "Hey! A little bird told me that you helped the Harpy Town!$1#$b#That's great news! You're so kind, @!$1#$b#I recommend trying açaí during summer, they make a great ice cream.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedMaru": "How interesting! I wonder what kinds of crazy specimens hide in the Harpy Town!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedPenny": "Let's hope the new kids get along together!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedCaroline": "I've heard the air there feels different...$1#$b#Maybe I should visit someday.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedClint": "*Gulp* I've seen a pretty girl in orange coming from the Harpy Town.$4#$b#D-do you think I have a chance?$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedDemetrius": "The Harpy Town has some interesting specimens of plants... It truly catches my interest.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedEvelyn": "Have you seen, sweetie? Joja cleared up the path to the Harpy Town!$1#$b#Finally I'll be able to see Mayara again.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedGeorge": "Hmph... Harpy Town... What's so interesting about it?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedGus": "I hope things are doing well with Raoni...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedJas": "...$3#$b#Do they have animals there?$3#$b#I saw a black kitten yesterday, do you think she lives there?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedJodi": "Maybe one day I'll visit Serena.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedKent": "A new area opened up...#$b#I'll have to stay alert.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedKrobus": "A new place filled with humans...#$b#I will observe from the shadows.",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedLeo": "Do you think they have any birds there?$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedLewis": "Ah, Harpy Town! It's been ages!$1#$b#This could be good for trade between communities.$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedLinus": "A new town, huh?...$1#$b#I hope they respect nature.$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedMarnie": "So sad they don't have any livestock there, I wish I could help somehow...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedPam": "Ah! I miss Mayara's good and ol' caipirinha!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedPierre": "Ah! New town, new possibilities to make money!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedRobin": "Hello there, @! I've heard that you helped Cida clear the path to the Harpy Town!#$b#That's great news! And I'll finally get to see my buddy Levi again!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedSandy": "How lovely of you to help Cida, dear!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedVincent": "I've heard there's a boy named Ravi, do you think he's cool?",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedWilly": "Aye! Say ''Hello'' to Julieta for me!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CTharpyTownUnlockedWizard": "I see you helped that old lady to remove the debris from the Harpy Town.#$b#I feel a strong energy coming from somewhere in the north of the village, be careful.",
    //
    //Vanilla gift tastes interactions
    //
    //Haley
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HaleyGTinteraction1": "For... Me?!$8#$b#Awwwww, @... It's beautiful! You shouldn't have...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HaleyGTinteraction2": "Mmmmm, so sweet and soft! Reminds me of pink cake! Thank you, @!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HaleyGTinteraction3": "This will be perfect for my skincare routine! Thank you, @!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HaleyGTinteraction4": "Ah! A perfume? For... Me?$8#$b#Thank you so much, @! It's even made of sunflowers!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_HaleyGTinteraction5": "*Gasp*! Is this perfume for me?$8#$b#Thank you so much, @! Charming pink cake... My favorite scent!$1",
