    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction3M": "Thank you, sweetheart! This perfume smells like a sunny afternoon!$1#$b#I Don't know if it makes sense to you, but it does to me, eheheheh...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction4M": "This perfume makes my head spin, but I can't stop smelling it...$3#$b#Don't worry, honey, I'm not complaining, I loved this gift!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction5M": "This perfume's name speaks for itself, it's fabulous! Eheheheh...$1#$b#Just like you...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction6M": "How sweet of you to bring me chocolates, dear! Bet this tastes delicious!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction7M": "It's been a while since I last ate this, brings back good old memories.$1#$b#Thank you for being the one who made me remember the good old times.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction8M": "The straw is shaped like a heart, how adorable.$4#$b#Silly things that you do like this are the ones that brighten my day, @.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction9M": "Thanks, honey! I would never say no to a little frozen treat!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction10M": "This will be perfect the next time I sit down to read. Thanks, honey!$1#$b#I hope I don't look silly wearing those...$2",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction11M": "This pen is so beautiful... And it will help me a lot in class! Thank you, honey!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction12M": "My bangs are always getting in my eyes when I'm reading, hopefully, this will help me!$1#$b#I love it when you think of me...",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction13M": "How adorable! It's pink and shaped like a heart!$1#$b#Mmmmm... The flavor is delicious too!$1#$b#Is this a demonstration of our love in a coffee?$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction14M": "There's something comforting about homemade sweets. And they taste even better when they're made by you.$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction15M": "*Gasp* How lovely of you, dear... I didn't know you were so good at knitting.$4#$b#Now I'll learn how to do it too, just to make a mini you, you just wait!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction16M": "This will be Mr. Rainbow, he'll be an emotional support for us and our new child! Ahahahah...$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction17M": "This tastes different from the desserts I'm used to.$3#$b#I think I like discovering new things like this, specially when they're made by you!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction18M": "It's so beautiful, @... Poppies are such lovely flowers... I love it when you bring them to me...$4",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_PennyGTinteraction19M": "How lovely of you, @...$4#$b#Now I feel like a princess, eheheh...$1#$b#Ah... Sorry if that sounded silly... Ahahahah...$1",
    //Caroline
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CarolineGTinteraction1": "Oh thank you, sweetie! Hehe it tickles my mouth!$1",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_CarolineGTinteraction2": "Ooooh remind me of green tea, I love it!$1",
    //Clint
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_ClintGTinteraction1": "For me? Thank you! I'm really fond of vegetables!$1",
