    //Demetrius
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_DemetriusGTinteraction1": "Is that... Arapaima?! One of the largest freshwater fish in the whole world?!$6#$b#Thank you, @, I shall study it closely.$3",
    "CheshiresAtelier.THTexpansion_DemetriusGTinteraction2": "Ah, pavê! It's been ages since I last ate one, thank you!$1#$b#Although I never understood the jokes people tell about it.$3#$b#I shall ask Robin.",
